Umubare w'abanduye indwara ya Koronavirusi (COVID-19) mu Burayi/Akarere ka Buraya no mu Bwongereza kuva ku wa 1 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abandura indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza imiterere nk'iyo mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, byemeza ko nubwo biri mu byiciro bitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri gutera imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Hashingiwe ku byaranze Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo nderabuzima bigomba kwitegura kurushaho icyorezo cy'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera kwitabwaho cyane cyane ku buryo bwimbitse.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, habonetse umubare munini w'abanduye icyorezo cya Pneumonia kitaramenyekana mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara mu Bushinwa cyatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari virusi nshya ya corona, ubu yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ibimenyetso kugeza ubu ni uko 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bagira uburwayi bworoheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bufite cyangwa budafite pneumonia, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14 ku ijana, COVID-19 iba icyorezo gikomeye, bisaba kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe abasigaye 6 ku ijana baba icyorezo gikomeye, gisaba kuvurwa cyane.
Urupfu rw'abarwayi bari mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye imiterere y'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'Uburayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza, maze tugereranya n'ibyabaye mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone kandi, twagereranyije umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'uw'u Butaliyani hagati y'itariki ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu karere, kandi imbaraga z'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ubu zikurikirana igihugu cy'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu igazeti ya Eurosurveillance 2020 yo ku ya 5 Werurwe, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko ari bo bantu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi, nk'uko bitangazwa na OMS.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'ubumwe bw'Akarere ka Buraya, abarwayi batatu ba mbere bemejwe batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bari bavuye i Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bari bamaze kugaragara mu bihugu byose 30 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Buraya n'u Bwongereza, aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza ku itariki yavuzwe haruguru, abantu 39,768 n'abapfuye 1,727 bari bamaze kumenyekana, muri bo 17,750 bakaba barapfuye 1,441 mu Butaliyani honyine.
Gushyiraho imibare y'ubwiyongere n'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19
Mu Kigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda (ECDC), umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi, ukomoka gusa ku makuru yemewe, nk'ubushikiranganji bw'ubuzima bw'ibihugu, abategetsi b'ubuzima mu bihugu no mu karere, na OMS, ushyirwa ahagaragara buri munsi saa munani z'amanywa.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Buraya n'u Bwongereza, no kuyigereranya n'iy'u Butaliyani.
Nk'igereranyo cy'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19, twabaze umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14, bityo dufata mu mutwe uko COVID-19 yagiye igenda muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone, twerekanye umubare munini w'abanduye muri buri gihugu kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani, tugereranya n'uw'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imiterere y'ubwiyongere bw'iminsi 14 y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, yakurikiye iyo mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Muri rusange, ku bihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abasoviyeti, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, buza kwiyongera cyane ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (inyongera).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'ubwandu bwavuzwe mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/umuryango w'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Area ya Aziya n'Ubwongereza byagaragaje imiterere nk'iyo yo kwiyongera kw'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 (inyandiko y'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Yemeza ko kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'ubumwe bw'iburayi n'Ubwongereza byari bimaze gutanga raporo y'umubare w'abanduye uhuza n'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu cyangwa munsi y'aho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abatangajwe ko banduye COVID-19 uri kwiyongera cyane mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Buraya n'Ubwongereza.
Imiterere igaragara mu mibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo gikomeje kugenda mu buryo busa mu bihugu byose.
Ibi ni byo nubwo ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, imikorere y'ubuvuzi rusange mu bihugu bitandukanye, kandi hashobora kuba hari ibisobanuro bitandukanye by'abandura mu bihugu bitandukanye, n'amabwiriza atandukanye agenga gutoranya abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo COVID-19 yemezwe, harimo no gupima kugira ngo haboneke amakuru agezweho.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twibasiwe n'icyorezo mu Butaliyani bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kuvurirwa mu bitaro bya intensive care, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indwara z'indwara za intensive care muri utwo turere byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwuzuye.
Amakuru ku barembye mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu byumba by'indembe kubera COVID-19 ubu araboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA kuri 6% na 1% by'abarembye gusa (amakuru atarerekanwa).
Ariko kandi, bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo buhoraho kugira ngo byongere ku makuru y'ubugenzuzi arimo, yibanda ku mubare w'abatangajwe n'umubare w'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe hagati ya 2010 na 2011 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu bubiko bw'ibitanda bya UTI n'ibyumba by'ubushakashatsi by'imashini z'ubushakashatsi mu Burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29,2 mu Budage kugeza ku bitanda 4,2 mu Butaliyani ku bantu 100 000.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira umutungo munini cyangwa muke ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 by'ibitanda by'ibitaro by'indwara z'ibicurane n'iby'ubushakashatsi bw'imbaraga nke ku baturage 100 000 hagati ya 2010 na 2011).
Imiterere y'ibishushanyo mbonera bijyanye no kuzura kw'ubushobozi bw'ishami ry'ubuzima, hamwe n'ingengo y'imari kuri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no ku Bwongereza y'ubwiyongere bw'abari mu bitaro bazira COVID-19 bafitanye isano n'ibyago byo kurenza 90% by'ubushobozi bw'ibitanda by'indembe, byatanzwe mu isesengura rya gatandatu ry'igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse rya ECDC kuri COVID-19.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu, abarwayi bakunze kugaragara mu turere tumwe na tumwe tw'ibihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'amavuriro ya ICU akenshi bikorera abaturage batoranyijwe mu karere, amakuru ku barwayi n'ibitaro bya ICU yagombye gutangwa mbere na mbere mu cyiciro cy'ibaruramari cy'uturere 2 (NUTS-2).
Urugero rw'Ubutaliyani n'imiterere mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirimo kugenda gihita mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubwisungane mu kwivuza bigomba rero kwitegura icyerekezo cy'ikwirakwizwa ry'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage no kwiyongera kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bw'indembe, nk'uko bigenda mu bice by'u Butaliyani byugarijwe n'iki cyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu isuzuma ry'ibiza byihuse rya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bwigenga kandi burambuye ni ingenzi mu guteza imbere ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2, hamwe no guhindura uburyo bwo kugabanya indwara, kuko kwiyongera k'umubare w'abandura bishobora kudahesha umwanya uhagije abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro kugira ngo basobanukirwe neza, bemere kandi bahindure ingamba zabo mu gihe badahise bashyira mu bikorwa.
Igenzura ry'ibyago byihuse ririmo kandi urutonde rw'ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari umwanya muto ibihugu bishobora kongera ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya igitutu ku rwego rw'ubuzima.
Iyo izo ngamba zirinzwe, birashoboka ko inzego z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu bya EU/EEA zizaba zifite abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus ya 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara ya coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS), kimaze kwica abantu barenga 3000 no kwandura abarenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bituma abantu bahura n'akaga.
Kimwe na virusi ya SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukwirakwira mu ducurama kandi igatera ibimenyetso nk'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Hagati aho, COVID-19 ifite ubukana buciriritse kandi buciriritse kurusha SARS, ariko ni indwara yandura cyane, kandi igera ku bantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko, kandi igera ku bagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza ku kwiyongera kwihuta kw'umubare w'ibitabo ku ndwara nshya, iyi nyandiko igamije gutanga isesengura ry'igihe kandi rirambuye ry'ikibazo cy'ubushakashatsi, gikomeje kwiyongera vuba.
Tuzasuzuma amahame y'ibanze y'indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu, izifata, izifata, izirwanya n'izirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko ubu bushakashatsi buzafasha mu gusobanukirwa no kurandura iyi ndwara iteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rudasanzwe kandi rutazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose bagombaga kuguma mu kato mu gihe cyose cy'iminsi mikuru ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi byakurikiyeho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara nshya y'ubwandu.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS) mu 2003; bityo, yashyizwe ku rutonde rwa SARS-CoV-2 n'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi iyi ndwara yahawe izina ry'indwara ya CoV-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, kandi cyakwirakwiriye mu gihugu hose mu buryo bwihuse, ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yari imaze gutuma haboneka abantu barenga 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abasaga 40.000 bakira, abasaga 3000 bakaba barapfuye.
OMS irakangurira ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere w'abaturage", kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hamaze gutangwa inyandiko zirenga 200 ku bijyanye na COVID-19, harimo virusi, indwara z'ibyorezo, izihuza n'imiterere y'umubiri, gusuzuma no kuvura, kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku wa 7 Mutarama 2020, yagaragaje ko virusi yavanywe mu barwayi batandukanye.
Iyi ngingo igamije gusobanura mu magambo make uko ubushakashatsi buhagaze muri ako gace gashya kagenda gahinduka vuba.
Aho bizaba bikenewe, tuzajya tugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, indwara yo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyo mu 2012).
Tuzasuzuma kandi ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana no kwirinda indwara no kuyigenzura, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo byihutirwa.
CoVs zisanzwe zifatwa nk'indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi zidateza abantu urupfu, ahanini zitera 15% bya za virusi z'ibicurane.
Hagati aho, muri iki kinyejana twabonye inshuro ebyiri za CoV z'abantu ziterwa n'indwara nyinshi, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye habaho icyorezo cyatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, nyuma zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi bifite uburwayi n'urupfu biteye ubwoba.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nkuko byagaragajwe ku ishusho ya Fig.1,1, igice cy'uburwayi bwa pneumonia butaramenyekana cyatangiriye kubwirwa Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'u Bushinwa i Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Hashize iminsi irindwi, urutonde rwa CoV rwarasohotse.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wapfuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu by'ibituranyi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, kwandura kw'abakozi b'ubuzima byatangajwe, byerekana ko kwandura hagati y'abantu bishoboka.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan wafunzwe, imodoka zose za Leta zihagarikwa.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere ku ndwara bwagaragaje ko ku barwayi 41 bemejwe ko banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bagiranye n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, ryashyizwe mu rwego rw'aho kwandurira byatangiriye biturutse ku nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu ku isi hose.
Kugeza ubu, iyi ndwara imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi (Igishushanyo (Fig.2).2).
Kubera ko ibintu birimo kwiyongera vuba, ikigero cy'icyorezo n'uburemere bwacyo by'imperuka biracyari gukorwa.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bigo bitandukanye ku barwayi 8,866, harimo 4,021 bemejwe ko barwaye COVID-19, bwagaragaje ishusho igezweho y'icyorezo nk'ikurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abantu b'imyaka yose, cyane cyane abari mu kigero cy'imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47,7%) cy'abanduye bari bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 50, bamwe bari munsi y'imyaka 20, kandi 14 gusa ni bo banduye bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abagabo benshi (0.31/100.000) kurusha abagore (0.27/100.000).
