Inkomoko ya za koronavirusi zo mu bantu
Guhinduka no guhinduka byateje ubwihindurize bwa koronavirusi (CoVs) n'abayirimo, harimo n'abantu, mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, byari bizwi ko virusi ebyiri za HCoV zitera indwara yoroheje, nk'ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ibyago by'indwara y'ubuhumekero bukomeye (SARS) na MERS (Middle East Respiratory Syndrome) byahinduye uko abantu batekerezaga kuri CoVs, kandi byerekana ko ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora kwica no kwangiza.
Igitero cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019 cyongeye gushyira CoVs mu mwanya wa mbere, gitangaza abantu bose kubera ko ishobora kwandura cyane kandi ikaba idafite ubukana bwo gutera indwara ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Uwanduza HCoV ni zoonotic, kandi gusobanukirwa inkomoko zoonotic ya HCoVs ni ingirakamaro cyane.
HCoVs nyinshi zituruka ku ducurama, aho zitandura.
Inzego z'ubutabazi z'abanduye HCoV zimwe na zimwe nazo zirazwi.
Kumenya inyamaswa zanduraho bigira ingaruka zigaragara ku kwirinda indwara mu bantu.
Gushakisha imikoranire ya CoV mu nyamaswa bishobora gutanga amakuru y'ingenzi ku bijyanye na pathogenesis ya CoV mu bantu.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twerekanye muri rusange amakuru ariho kuri HCoVs ndwi, twibanda ku mateka yo kuvumburwa kwayo, hamwe n'inkomoko yayo mu nyamaswa no gukwirakwira hagati y'amoko.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ingenzi ni ugupima no kugereranya HCoV zitandukanye, tubikesha iterambere ry'ubwandu n'uburyo genome ihinduranya.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya CoV 2019 (COVID-19) kirimo kirasuzumwa muri iyi nkuru.
Byongeye kandi, ibisabwa kugira ngo virusi ishobore guhinduka neza hagati y'abayirinda ndetse n'ingaruka zo guhinduka kwa virusi ku burwayi, nabyo byashimangiwe.
Koronavirusi (CoVs) ni zo mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'ubwandu bwa virusi bufite ubwiza bw'ubwiza n'ubw'urusobe rw'ubwoko bumwe bwa RNA.
Izo virusi zifite genome nini cyane, hagati ya 26 na 32 kilobases, mu virusi za RNA zahawe izina rya "CoVs" kubera imiterere ya corona yazo iyo zibonekerwa mu kigororangingo cya elegitoroniki.
Ku birebana n'imiterere, CoVs zifite genomes zitari mu byiciro bitandukanye, zigira gahunda imwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya genome birimo imiterere ibiri y'ibisobanuro by'ibisobanuro by'ibisobanuro (ORF1a na ORF1b), bihindurwa muri pp1a na pp1ab.
Polyproteins zongera gutunganywa, maze zikagira poroteyine 16 zitari iz'ibanze, zitwa nsp1 kugeza ku nsp16.
Igice gisigaye cya genome kirimo ORFs z'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze birimo spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Hari poroteyine zimwe na zimwe z'inyongera z'ubwoko runaka nazo zandikwa n'ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV.
Hashingiwe ku itandukaniro ry'ibinyabuzima, CoVs zashyizwe mu miryango ine (alfaCoV, betaCoV, gammaCoV na deltaCoV), muri yo, betaCoV irimo abenshi mu ba HCoVs kandi igabanyijemo imiryango ine (A, B, C na D).
Ibimenyetso by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byerekanye ko udukoko n'imbeba ari byo bitanga ibinyabuzima byinshi bya alphaCoVs na betaCoVs, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga cyane cyane gammaCoVs na deltaCoVs.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs zakomeje kunyura mu nzego z'ibanze z'ibinyabuzima, kandi zimwe muri zo zabaye indwara z'ingenzi zibasira abantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana abantu barindwi bafite virusi ya koronavirusi (HCoVs).
Muri byo, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni alphaCoVs.
Izindi betaCoV eshanu zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, virusi ya coronavirus y'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS-CoV), virusi ya coronavirus y'indwara ifata imyakura yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV), na SARS-CoV-2.
Virusi HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'imbeho isanzwe n'ibicurane.
Ku rundi ruhande, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 iherutse kuvugwa ni indwara zandura cyane, kandi zitera indwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero bwo hasi mu barwayi benshi, bafite amahirwe menshi yo kugira ikibazo cy'ubuhumekero bukabije (Acute Respiratory Discomfort Syndrome - ARDS) n'ibindi byorezo byo hanze y'ibihaha.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwiciwe mu mubiri w'abarwayi ba saruwasi isanzwe mu myaka ya za 60.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi bwinshi bwakozwe binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse ku cyorezo cya HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bikaba bitera ibimenyetso byigenga.
Mu by'ukuri, igitekerezo cy'uko ubwandu bwa HCoVs busanzwe butagira icyo butwara cyari cyemewe cyane kugeza mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya SARS.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byangije cyane kurusha ibindi muri iki gihe, cyanduje abantu barenga ibihumbi umunani, ku gipimo cy'urupfu rw'abantu 10 ku ijana.
Imyaka icumi nyuma yaho, icyorezo cya MERS (Middle East Respiratory Syndrome) cyatumye habaho icyorezo gikomeje muri Arabiya, kigakwira hirya no hino ku isi.
HCoV nshya yo mu 2019 (2019-nCoV), yaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo iteza icyorezo cya coronavirus yo mu 2019 (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana ubuzima bw'abantu barenga 3,120 no kwandura abantu barenga 91.000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Umutekano urimo guhuha, kandi isi ikeneye kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kigiye kuza.
HCoVs zose uko ari ndwi zituruka mu nyamaswa mu mikinnyi, imbeba cyangwa amatungo yo mu ngo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi byemeza ko HCoVs zose zakomotse ku ducurama, aho virusi zisanzwe ziteye neza kandi zidakomoka ku ndwara, ariko zigaragaza ko zinyuranye mu buryo bw'imiterere.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gitanga imbogamizi zikomeye mu buvuzi, siyansi, imibereho n'umuco ku Bushinwa no ku isi yose.
Gukurikirana inkomoko ya zoonoti ya HCoVs bitanga igishushanyo mbonera cyo gusobanukirwa amateka y'ibidukikije, imbaraga zituma virusi ihungabana n'impamvu zituma ikwirakwira mu zindi ndwara.
Ibi kandi bishobora kuyobora no koroshya ishakishwa ry'abari bakingira, abahuza n'abagura SARS-CoV-2, bigira ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira mu gihe kizaza ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu hagati y'amoko.
Muri iyi ngingo, dutanga isesengura ry'inkomoko y'ibinyabuzima, ikwirakwira hagati y'amoko n'imiterere y'indwara ziterwa na HCoVs.
By'umwihariko, twasobanuye kandi tuganira ku ngingo rusange ivuga ko virusi z'ababyeyi za HCoVs zidakunda gutera indwara mu ngo z'ibanze, ariko ko zikomeza gutera indwara nyuma yo kwanduzwa mu bwoko butandukanye ku wundi muntu.
Nanone kandi, twasuzumye uko HCoV yagiye itera, aho ubwandu bwagendaga bwiyongera, akenshi bikagendana no kugabanuka kw'imikorere y'indwara.
Uko icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kirangiye nabyo biravugwa muri iyi nkuru.
CoV z'amatungo zamenyekanye kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30.
Mbere yo kuvana bwa mbere ubwoko bwa B814 bwa HCoV-229E mu mubiri w'abarwayi bafashe ibicurane, hari izindi virusi za CoV zari zaravumbuwe mu nyamaswa nyinshi zanduye, harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, injangwe n'imbwa.
Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, hamaze kuvumburwa virusi zirindwi za HCoV.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka igera kuri mirongo itanu, abantu benshi bakunze kwibasirwa n'uburwayi bw'ibicurane, ariko ntibashobore kubwisuzuma.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E bwatoranyijwe mu buryo bwo guhumeka bw'abarwayi bafite ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru mu mwaka wa 1966, nyuma buza gukoreshwa mu mikurire mu miterere y'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu maraso ya WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'ibicurane birimo umutwe, gusinzira, uburwayi bw'amarira n'umuhogo, hamwe n'umuriro n'igicuri byibonekeje mu 10% kugeza kuri 20% by'abanduye.
Nyuma yaho mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yavanywe mu binyabuzima by'ibihimba by'umubiri no mu bwonko bw'imbeba ziryamye.
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bwa HCoV-OC43 bisa n'ibyaterwa na HCoV-229E, bidatandukanye n'ibindi byorezo by'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane bya influenza A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 zikwirakwizwa ku isi hose, kandi zikunze gukwirakwizwa cyane cyane mu gihe cy'imbeho mu bihe by'ubushyuhe.
Muri rusange, igihe cyo gukingirwa kwa izi virusi zombi ni munsi y'icyumweru kimwe, kizaherekezwa n'indwara mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ubushakashatsi bwakorewe ku bantu bitangiye gukora imirimo, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye HCoV-229E bagize ikibazo cy'ubukonje bworoheje.
Gusa abarwayi bake bafite ubwirinzi budafite ingufu ni bo bagaragaje ubwandu bukomeye bw'ubuhumekero bwo hasi.
SARS, nanone izwi nka "atypical pneumonia", ni yo yari icyorezo cya mbere cyanditswe cyatewe na HCoV mu mateka y'umuntu, kandi icyorezo cyatewe na SARS-CoV, ni cyo cya gatatu cya HCoV cyatangiye kuvumburwa.
Umuntu wa mbere wahuye na SARS yavutse mu 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje abantu 8,096 batangajwe ko banduye ndetse 774 bakicwa, kikaba cyarafashe ibihugu byinshi n'ibihugu bitandukanye.
Uretse "abanduye cyane", byatekerejwe ko umuntu umwe ufite ubwandu ashobora kwanduza abandi babiri, afite iminsi 4 kugeza ku minsi 7, kandi ku munsi wa 10 w'indwara, virusi iba imaze kugera ku ndunduro yayo.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV babanje kugaragaza uburibwe, umutwe, umuriro, uburwayi n'imihangayiko, bikurikirwa n'ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero, guhekenya no guhumeka nabi.
Lymphopenia, ikibazo cy'umwijima n'uburwayi bwa creatine kinase ni ibintu bisanzwe by'indwara ya SARS mu bipimo byo mu ma laboratwari.
Ibyangiritse mu gitereko by'amaraso, kwiyongera kw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'uruhu no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'ibinyabiziga by'uruhu nabyo biraboneka mu barwayi ba SARS.
Hafi 20% kugeza kuri 30% by'abarwayi baba bakeneye kuvurwa cyane no guhumeka.
Usibye uburyo bwo guhumeka bwo hasi, ingingo zitandukanye zirimo imyanya y'ubuhumekero, impyiko n'impyiko, nazo zishobora kugira ingaruka muri ibi bihe bikomeye, akenshi hakagira urujya n'uruza rw'ibinyabutabire, bishobora kwica, cyane cyane mu barwayi bafite ubwirinzi budafite ingufu.
Virusi ya mbere yabonetse mu isuzuma ry'ibihaha by'umuvandimwe wa Patient Zero wari utwaye imodoka ava i Guangzhou ajya i Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, hashyizweho imbaraga nyinshi mu bushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yavanywe mu mwana w'amezi 7 mu Buholandi mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2004.
Byabonetse bwa mbere ko virusi yari yiganje mu bana bato, abageze mu za bukuru n'abarwayi bafite uburwayi bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero butarangwa n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Ibimenyetso by'indwara y'umusonga, konjontivite, umuriro n'indwara y'ibihaha ni ibisanzwe mu ndwara iterwa na HCoV-NL63.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwigenga bwagaragaje ko virusi imwe yavanywe mu musaya w'umwana w'amezi 8 wari urwaye pneumonia mu Buholandi.
Nubwo byamenyekanye mu Buholandi, byiganje hirya no hino ku isi.
HCoV-NL63 yagereranyijwe ko ari hafi 4.7% by'indwara zisanzwe zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, kandi ubwandu bwayo bugera ku kigero cyo hejuru mu itumba, mu itumba no mu ntangiriro z'impeshyi.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano na laryngitis obstructive, nanone izwi nka croup.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yavanywe mu mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari mu bitaro arwaye pneumonia na bronchiolitis muri Hong Kong.
Uretse uburwayi bwa pneumonia n'uburwayi bwa bronchiolitis bw'abaturage, HCoV-HKU1 yavuzwe ko ifitanye isano no kongera uburwayi bw'igicuri.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yabonetse ku isi hose, ituma abantu barwara indwara z'ubuhumekero zidakira.
Izo HCoV zose uko ari enye zaturutse mu baturage zisanzwe zihuza neza n'abantu kandi muri rusange nta bushobozi zifite bwo guhinduka no gutera indwara zandura cyane, nubwo impanuka zabaye ku mpamvu zitazwi mu rubanza rutarigera rubaho rw'ubwoko bw'ubwoko bwa HCoV-NL63 bufite ubukana bwinshi, buherutse kuvugwa ko butera indwara ikomeye yo mu muhogo wo hasi mu Bushinwa.
Muri rusange, iyo izi HCoV zifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira neza kandi zikaguma mu bantu, na zo ziba zidafite ubukana kandi zidakwirakwiza indwara.
MERS-CoV yabonetse bwa mbere mu 2012 mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wagize indwara y'ibicurane n'impyiko mu gihugu cya Arabiya Sawudite.
Mu gihe abenshi mu bantu bagaragaye ko banduye bakekwaho gukora ibizamini bakomoka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, hari abandi bantu baturuka mu bindi bihugu by'i Burayi na Tuniziya bagiye bagaragazwa ko banduye bakwirakwira mu buryo bw'ibanze.
Indi ndwara ya kabiri yabereye muri Koreya y'Epfo mu 2015 aho abantu 186 bemejwe ko banduye.
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bwa MERS bisa n'ibya SARS, birangwa n'uburwayi bw'ibicurane by'ubuhumekero.
Bitandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi ba MERS nabo bagira uburwayi bw'impyiko, bityo bikaba ari ibintu bidasanzwe kuri MERS mu ndwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarenga 30% by'abarwayi bagira ibimenyetso byo mu gifu, urugero nk'ibicurane no kwitsamura.
