Ku bw'ibyo, ntibishoboka ko ingamiya zose zicwa kugira ngo MERS ihagarare nk'uko byagenze mu masoko y'inyamaswa zo mu ishyamba mu Bushinwa kugira ngo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zitandukana.
Kugira ngo haboneke umuti w'icyorezo cya MERS cyongera kugaruka, hakwiye gushyirwaho uburyo buhagije bwo gukora inkingo z'urukingo rwa MERS-CoV mu ngamiya, zifatanyije n'izindi ngamba zo kugenzura ubwandu.
Kubera ko tudashobora kurandura izo virusi, hari ubundi bwoko bushya bushobora kuvuka bugateza ibyorezo.
Hari ubwoko bwinshi bwa CoVs zo mu nyamaswa zinyuranye zikwirakwira mu gisekuru.
By'umwihariko, CoVs z'ibinyugunyugu bifite ubushobozi bwo kwanduza inyamaswa zitandukanye cyane.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo ko izi CoV zo mu nyamaswa zishobora guhinduka no kongera guhuza, bigatuma habaho izindi CoV nshya zishobora kwandura cyane kandi/cyangwa zikaba zishe abantu mu gihe kizaza.
Umuco wo kurya inyamaswa mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'Ubushinwa ugomba gucibwa kugira ngo abantu n'inyamaswa batagirana imishyikirano idakenewe.
Mu gihe hazabaho ibibazo bya SARS, MERS na COVID-19, hategerejwe uburyo bwiza bwo kwitegura no guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Mu by'ukuri, virusi nyinshi zabayeho ku isi kuva kera cyane.
Baguma mu byaro byabo kugeza igihe habonekeye uburyo bwo kwimukira mu kindi gisekuru.
Nubwo udusimba dufite ibintu byinshi bidufasha gukwirakwiza virusi, amahirwe y'uko abantu bahura n'udusimba n'izindi nyamaswa zo mu gasozi ashobora kugabanuka cyane iyo abantu bigishijwe kubirinda.
Kugenzura guhoraho mu nyamaswa z'ibinyabuzima ni ngombwa kugirango dusobanukirwe neza ibidukikije bya CoVs n'abaturanyi bayo, bizagufasha mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'inyamaswa ku bantu no mu gihe kizaza.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bwiza bwo gukumira virusi ya zoonosis ni uko abantu bakomeza kuba kure y'ibibanza byo mu bidukikije birimo za virusi z'ibinyabuzima.
Ibice byinshi by'ikibazo cy'inkomoko y'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 biracyari kubura.
Icya mbere, niba udusimba twanduza virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 y'abasekuruza ku ducurama, ni ngombwa kumenya imimerere udusimba n'udusimba bishobora kuba biherereyeho.
Icya kabiri, niba inkoko zifite uruhare rw'ibanze mu kwanduza abantu, uburyo abantu bahura n'inkoko bugomba kugenzurwa.
Icya gatatu, niba inyamaswa ya gatatu ifite uruhare rw'umunyamuryango nyawe, hakenewe gusobanurwa uburyo ikorana n'amoko atandukanye, harimo abantu, udusimba n'ibinyamushongo.
Amaherezo, kubera ko inyamaswa nyinshi zinyamaswa, harimo n'inyamaswa zo mu ngo, zishobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2, hagomba gukorwa igenzura no gupima.
Niba ari umukangara, ingunguru cyangwa ikindi kinyamaswa cy'amafi, birateganyijwe ko SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa virusi z'ababyeyi bayo zimeze kimwe bizagaragara mu byaremwe mu gihe kizaza.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeje muri iki gice buzatuma haboneka isomo ku nzira y'ihindagurika rya SARS-CoV-2 mu nyamaswa, bigatuma abantu barushaho kwirinda no kugenzura COVID-19.
Hakenewe kuvugurura ibipimo byo gupima "ukekwaho" na "ukemezwaho" COVID-19
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryashyize ahagaragara igitabo cy'ubuyobozi bwihuse ku gupima no kuvura ubwandu bwa coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV). Icyo gitabo cyerekana ubunararibonye bwacu kandi ni icyerekezo cyiza cyo kurwanya iki cyorezo cyugarije isi.
Nyamara, indwara ya coronavirus ya 2019 (COVID-19) ni nshya. Gusobanukirwa no kumenya kwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bishingiye ku bushakashatsi buhoraho no kugerageza mu buvuzi; kubera iyo mpamvu, uburyo bwo gupima no kuvura nabwo burakomeza kuvugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije igitekerezo ku cyerekezo cyacu, kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya byo gupima "kekwa" na "kemezwa" hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya y'ubuvuzi n'ubuvuzi bwa COVID-19 (igice cya karindwi) yashyizwe ahagaragara na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y'Ubushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yateje icyorezo, ubu cyitwa coronavirus y'indwara ya 2019 (COVID-19), kandi virusi yitwa coronavirus 2 y'indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yashyize COVID-19 mu byiciro bya pandemic.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 yanduye, itsinda ryacu ryakoze igitabo cy'ubuyobozi cyihuse cyasohotse kuri interineti mu kinyamakuru cya Military Medical Research ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020.
Kuva yasohoka, yagiye ituma abantu benshi bayifashisha.
Ariko kandi, wibuke ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya. Gusobanukirwa no kumenya kwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bishingiye ku byo ubushakashatsi bukomeza kuvumbura no ku byerekeranye n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi; kubera iyo mpamvu, uburyo bwo gupima no kuvura na bwo bugenda buvugururwa buri gihe.
Urugero, Amabwiriza yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 yashyizwe ahagaragara na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika ya Rubanda y'u Bushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020 afite impinduka zigera kuri zirindwi, zimwe muri zo zikaba zarahinduye imiterere.
Ubuyobozi bwacu bwasohoye igitekerezo cyatanzwe na Zhou et al., watanze igitekerezo cyoroshye gishingiye ku byaranze ubuvuzi bwe.
Iki gikorwa cyongereye ibindi bimenyetso bishya ku buyobozi bwacu kandi kirimo n'ibisobanuro by'agaciro kuri iki cyorezo cyugarije isi.
Turashyigikiye umurimo wawe w'ingenzi kandi turagushimira.
Hagati aho, akazi kabo kandi gakeneye kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya y'igenzura no kuvura COVID-19 (igenzura rya karindwi) n'ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'Igitabo cya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo umuntu yemeze ko ari umuntu ukekwaho uburwayi, bisaba guhuza kimwe mu bintu by'amateka y'indwara n'ibintu bibiri by'uburwayi kugira ngo hakorwe isesengura rirambuye, cyangwa se bisaba kubahiriza ibintu bitatu by'uburwayi mu gihe nta mateka y'indwara asobanutse:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'ingendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu duce tuwurimo cyangwa mu yindi midugudu aho abarwayi ba COVID-19 bagaragaye mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka; (2) amateka y'abahuye n'abarwayi ba SARS-CoV-2 (bafite ADN yemeza); (3) amateka y'abahuye n'abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu duce tuwurimo cyangwa mu yindi midugudu aho abarwayi ba COVID-19 bagaragaye mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka; (4) amateka y'abahuye n'abantu bafite icyorezo (barenze cyangwa bangana n'abarwayi babiri bafite umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero byabaye mu byumweru 2 mu byumba bito, nko mu rugo, mu biro, mu ishuri, n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) ku buryo bwo gupima indwara ya COVID-19; (3) umubare w'amaraso yera yose agaragaza umubare usanzwe, wagabanyijwe cyangwa wagabanyijwe w'amaraso mu gihe cy'intangiriro y'ibimenyetso.
Gushakisha icyorezo cyemejwe bigomba gushingira ku gukekwaho kimwe muri ibi bikurikira: (1) isuzuma rya PCR ryemeza SARS-CoV-2; (2) gukusanya genomic yuzuye yerekana ko ifite homogenization nyinshi ku ndwara nshya za coronavirus; (3) igaragaza IgM na IgG by'umwihariko kuri SARS-CoV-2 mu isuzuma rya serum; cyangwa igaragaza IgG by'umwihariko kuri SARS-CoV-2 bivuye ku by'umwihariko cyangwa bikuraho inshuro enye cyangwa zirenze mu cyiciro cyo gukira.
Turabona ko isuzuma rya PCR mu gihe nyacyo ku byerekeye aside ya nucleic mu bipimo by'amaraso cyangwa mu bwonko byongerewe ku cyiciro cya kabiri n'icya gatatu (ku ya 18 na 22 Mutarama 2020, hakurikijwe uko byakozwe).
Gusuzuma indwara ziterwa n'amaraso byongerewe ku ncuro ya kane n'iya gatanu (ku ya 27 Mutarama 2020 na 8 Gashyantare 2020), naho ibipimo bya serology byongerwa ku ya karindwi.
Izo mpinduka zishingiye ku gikorwa gikomeje gukorwa n'abashakashatsi mu gushaka igikoresho cyiza cyo gupima aside ya nucleic acid mu gupima vuba, no mu gupima ibipimo byo mu muhogo w'ubuhumekero, harimo no gupima amaraso, byongereye iboneka ry'ibipimo bitandukanye kandi bifasha mu gutuma haboneka ingirabuzimafatizo zihariye ku bipimo byemejwe.
Byongeye kandi, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bidufasha kwibuka kwita ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso n'abatabifite.
Niyo mpamvu, igishushanyo mbonera cya Zhou et al. kigomba kuvugururwa kuko kigaragaza umuntu udafite ibimenyetso byo mu buvuzi nk'umuntu ufite ibyago bike.
Sisitemu yo kubara nayo ikeneye kwemezwa mu zindi nyigo no mu buvuzi.
Mu gusoza, turategereje ko hagira ibindi bimenyetso by'ibanze biboneka, kandi turasaba abasomyi gutanga ibitekerezo byabo.
Ku bijyanye no gusuzuma "ukekwaho" n'"ukemezwaho", turabasaba ko mwareba kandi mukumvira amabwiriza agezweho mu bihugu byanyu.
Abakozi bacu kandi bazajya basubiramo ubuyobozi bwacu mu gihe gikwiriye kugira ngo badufashe.
Bangladesh yatangaje abantu batanu bashya bapfuye bazira COVID-19, umubare munini ku munsi
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje abantu bashya batanu bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19 ku munsi.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye mu munsi umwe kubera virusi.
Ku munsi w'ejo, Ikigo cya Epidemiology, Disease Control and Research cyo muri Bangladesh (IEDCR) cyatangaje ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura uyu muti ugizwe n'abarwayi 114 bari ku kazi, naho 33 bagarutse bagasigara mu rugo.
Hamaze kwandikwa abantu 17 bapfuye.
Mu makuru yo kuri interineti, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko abapfuye barimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dukurikije uko Dr. Meerjady abivuga, babiri bari bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 60, babiri bari bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 51 na 60, n'undi wari ufite imyaka iri hagati ya 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko babiri mu baguye muri icyo gitero bakomokaga i Dhaka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe.
Umukozi w'ibitaro yabwiye Anadolu Agency, ikinyamakuru cy'amakuru cyo muri ako gace, ko umwe mu bapfuye ari Jalal Saifur Rahman, umuyobozi wa Komisiyo yo kurwanya ruswa muri Bengali, wavurirwaga mu bitaro bya Kuwait Maitree.
Ku wa gatandatu, mu itangazo ryanyuze kuri interineti, Minisitiri w'umuhanda n'ibiraro Obaidul Quader yavuze ko imodoka za Leta zizamara igihe kirekire kurusha uko byari byarateganyijwe kugeza ku wa Gatandatu utaha.
Uku guhagarika ingendo za rubanda byatangiye ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, byari biteganyijwe ko bizarangira ku wa Gatandatu tariki ya 4 Mata.
Itwara ry'ibikoresho by'ibanze (imiti, lisansi n'ibiribwa) ryari rikiri ryemewe.
Abantu ba mbere banduye COVID-19 muri Bangladesh bavugwa ku itariki ya 8 Werurwe, mu bantu babiri bari bavuye mu Butaliyani, ndetse no mu mugore w'umwe muri bo.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, bose uko ari batatu bari barakize.
SARS-CoV-2 irenga miliyoni y'ubwandu ku isi
Ku wa kane, umubare w'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 ku isi bose warenze miliyoni, nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ibaruramari rya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Nibura abantu 52,000 bapfuye bashingiye kuri COVID-19, indwara iterwa na coronavirus.
Iki kimenyetso cyaje ku munsi umwe Malawi yemeje ubwandu bwa mbere bwa coronavirus na Zambia ifite urupfu rwa mbere rufitanye isano na virusi.
Koreya ya Ruguru yavuze ko kugeza ku wa kane ari kimwe mu bihugu bike bisigaye bitanduye coronavirus.
Kugeza ejo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko abantu 1,051,635 bamaze kwandura, harimo 79,332 mu masaha 24 mbere ya saa kumi (0800 UTC) ku itariki ya 4 Mata.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, hamaze kwandura abantu barenga 244.000 banduye coronavirus, bihitana abantu bagera ku 5.900.
