Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryemeje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19  indwara iterwa na koronavirusi SARS-CoV-2  ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "pandemic" rigaragaza gusa uko indwara ikwirakwira, ntabwo ari uburyo izi ndwara zihariye ari mbi, OMS yashimangiye ko ari ngombwa gushishikariza leta kugira icyo zikora:
Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyerekezo cy'iki cyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze ko ibihugu bishobora gupima, gupima, kuvura, gushyira mu kato, gukurikirana no guhuza abaturage kugira ngo bagire icyo bakora.
Dufite impungenge nyinshi ku rugero rugayitse rw'ubwandu n'uburemere bwabwo ndetse n'urugero rugayitse rw'uko nta cyo abantu bakora.
Dukurikije uko Dr. Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda abivuga, ni icyorezo "kitigeze kibaho mbere hose".
Mu magambo yashyizwe ahagaragara na CNN muri Gashyantare, yavuze ko "nta zindi virusi z'ubuhumekero zigeze zikurikiranwa kuva zisanzwe zikwirakwira ku isi hose".
Ghebreyesus yavuze ibintu nk'ibyo, avuga ko "nta cyorezo cyatangijwe na koronavirusi twigeze tubona".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi ntitwabonye icyorezo cyashoboraga kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
Iyi ndwara nshya y'icyorezo ikurikiye icyemezo cyafashwe na OMS muri Mutarama cyo gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu mpuzamahanga.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara z'Akarwara n'Amasuzuguro, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko icyo cyorezo "mu magambo make, kizagenda kirushaho kuba kibi".
Ku wa kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko nibura hari abantu 126.000 banduye COVID-19 ku isi hose, aho abantu barenga 4.600 bapfuye.
Icyorezo cya 201920 cya Coronavirus ni icyorezo gikomeje cy'indwara ya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na Coronavirus y'indwara ifata imyakura yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ikomeye 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangajwe ko ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu mpuzamahanga ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama 2020 ndetse cyemezwa ko ari icyorezo ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, aho abagera ku 97.000 bapfuye.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
