Icyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye ry'ubukungu n'imibereho ku isi, gusubikwa cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa bya siporo, iby'idini, ibya politiki n'umuco, no kubura ibicuruzwa byogeye, byongereweho n'ubucuruzi bwatewe n'ubwoba.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunze ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa rw'akarere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku banyeshuri bagera kuri 99,4% ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo kuri virusi yageze kuri interineti, kandi habaye ibikorwa byo kwanga abanyamahanga no kubarenganya, byibasira Abashinwa, abantu bakomoka mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Uburasirazuba bwa Aziya n'abandi baturutse mu turere dufite abarwayi benshi ba virusi.
