Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe, kandi abantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara cyane ni umuriro (88%) n'igisebo cyumye (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara harimo umunaniro, gutakaza umwuka (guterwa n'umuyaga), kubura impumuro, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu myuniko no mu ngingo, kubabara mu muhogo, kubabara umutwe, gutekenyera, kwitsamura, guhumeka, guhumeka, gucibwamwo, gucibwamwo cyangwa cyanoze.
