Bamwe mu bantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso, nta bimenyetso byo mu buvuzi bafite, ariko bakaba bafite ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi bagasaba ko abahuye n'umuntu ufite ubwandu bwahamijwe ko bagomba gukurikiranwa hafi no gusuzumwa kugira ngo basuzume niba nta bwandu bafite.
