Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije inganda no mu nganda kongera gufungura ku wa 30 Werurwe, itanga ibyangombwa by'inguzanyo ku nganda. Inama y'igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kuboroga, utangira ku isaha ya saa tatu z'amanywa ku itariki ya 4 Mata, mu gihe cya Qingming Festival.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, hemejwe ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 mu Bushinwa igera muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko habonetse ubwandu bwinshi ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, ahanini bikaba byatewe n'uko mu mujyi wa Daegu habereye inama y'ishyaka rishya ry'idini ryitwa Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abantu bashidikanya ko Shincheonji wasuraga Daegu avuye i Wuhan ariwe watumye iki cyorezo gitangira.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iri dini, 1,261, cyangwa hafi 13% muri bo, batangaje ko bafite ibimenyetso.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, havuzwe abantu barenga 2000 bemejwe ko banduye, ku ya 29 Gashyantare habonekaga abantu 3.150.
Ibigo bya gisirikare byose byo muri Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bapimwe bagasanga banduye virusi.
Ibihe by'indege nabyo byagize ingaruka kandi birahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho icyo bitaga gahunda nini kandi iteguwe neza ku isi mu bijyanye no gupima abaturage virusi. Igihugu cyashyize mu kato abantu banduye kandi cyakurikirana no gushyira mu kato abahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima harimo no gutanga raporo ku giti cyabo ku bantu bageraga mu bihugu bitandukanye bakoresheje porogaramu ya telefoni igendanwa, gupima virusi hakoreshejwe imodoka, ku munsi ukurikiyeho, ndetse no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima, byemerera abantu bagera ku 20.000 gupimwa ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'iy'ibanze mu kugenzura iki cyorezo, nubwo itashyize imijyi yose mu kato.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon yahagarikwa ku byaha by'ubutegetsi, bavuga ko ari uko ubutegetsi bwe butarimo gucunga neza iki cyorezo, cyangwa se bagashimagiza uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo yari ifite umubare muto w'abanduye mu byumweru bine.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bashya bavuye mu mahanga bagomba kumara ibyumweru bibiri mu kato.
Ibinyamakuru byo ku itariki ya 1 Mata byatangaje ko Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye abantu bo mu bihugu 121 biyifuzagaho ubufasha mu gupima virusi.
Irani yemeje abarwayi bayo ba mbere ba SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 19 Gashyantare mu mujyi wa Qom, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi yavuze ko abantu babiri bapfuye uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, siporo n'ibikorwa by'idini ku wa gatanu, gufunga kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani ifite trilioni eshanu za riyal zo kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda afite ku bice by'abatuye mu kato byibasiwe n'icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Imyiteguro yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwinshi hagati y'imijyi mbere y'umwaka mushya wa Nouruz wakomeje.
Ahantu hatagatifu h'Abashia i Qom hagumye hagaragara ku bayoboke b'idini rya Isilamu kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Hagati y'ibirego byo guhishira aho iki cyorezo cyageze muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byakurikiranye abarwayi bacyo ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, bivuga ko iki cyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha 388 leta ya Irani yari imaze gutangaza.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, aho 23 mu banyamuryango bayo 290 bapimwe ko banduye virusi ya Corona tariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye cyane abayobozi ba gereza za Irani gufungura byimazeyo abarwanashyaka b'uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira kwigomeka mu mahoro, no gufungura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira.
Urwego rwavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi mu bigo bifunze nk'ibigo byo gufungirwamo, nabyo bibabara kubera kubura ubuvuzi.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, umubare munini kuva icyorezo cyatangira muri icyo gihugu.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 bari ku butegetsi cyangwa abamaze ikiruhuko cy'izabukuru n'abakozi ba leta bapfuye bazize iyo ndwara.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha n'urupfu rushya buri minota 10 kubera coronavirus.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi wa OMS, muri Irani hari abantu bakubye inshuro eshanu abo bivugwa ko banduye.
Hari abavuga ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kuba bigira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'imari bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Komiseri Mukuru w'Uburenganzira bwa Muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanywa ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo ba mukerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bapimwaga ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Abarwayi batangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose zijya n'izava mu Bushinwa, ndetse itangaza ko ari mu bihe by'ubukungu.
Itsinda ritari rifitanye isano n'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ryongeye kugaragara nyuma, ritangirana n'abarwayi 16 bemejwe muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rigenga kurwanya iki cyorezo, harimo no gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50.000 baturutse mu mirenge 11 itandukanye mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Mu turere dufite icyorezo, abantu ntibemererwa kwinjira no gusohoka.
Gufunga ibikorwa by'akazi n'imikino byari byamaze gushyirwaho muri utwo turere. "Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yasabye ko amashuri yose na kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu cyose ubwo Ubutaliyani bwageraga ku bantu 100 bapfuye.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya Serie A, yagombaga kubera mu nzu z'abakinnyi kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe burundu nibura ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yasabye ko ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi bifungwa, usibye amaduka manini n'amafashanyigisho. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ishuri ry'Ubutaliyani ry'ubuvuzi, ubuvuzi, ubutabazi n'ubuvuzi bukomeye (SIAARTI) ryasohoye inama z'imibanire y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye na protokoli zo gupima zishobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwatsinze Ubushinwa nk'igihugu gifite umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye bazira Coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga amakuru y'abantu 3,405 bapfuye bazira icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'igisirikare zitwaye imiti mu Butaliyani.
Kuva ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari hamaze kugaragara abantu 128,948, hapfa 15,887 naho abakize 21,815, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko guhuza abaturage bageze mu za bukuru bo mu Butaliyani n'ubushobozi bwo kudashobora gupima abantu bose bari baranduye virusi kugeza icyo gihe bishobora kuba byaratumye habaho igipimo cyo hejuru cy'abapfa.
Igisubizo cy'u Bwongereza kuri virusi cyabonetse bwa mbere nk'ikintu cyoroshye kurusha ibindi mu bihugu byibasiwe, kandi kugeza ku itariki ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'u Bwongereza ntiyigeze ishyiraho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutandukanya abantu cyangwa gushyira abantu mu kato ku bwinshi.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, leta yanenzwe kubera kubura ubushishozi no kutagira imbaraga mu gusubiza ibibazo byugarije abaturage. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatanze itangazo rigira inama yo guhagarika ingendo zose zidakenewe no gutumanaho, agasaba abantu gukora mu rugo uko bishoboka kose no kwirinda ahantu nk'inshuti, resitora n'ibikino.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro nka pubs na gyms bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi yiyemeza kwishyura 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi kugeza ku gipimo cya £ 2.500 buri kwezi kugirango wirinde ubushomeri mugihe cy'ihungabana. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gutandukanya abantu, kubuza abantu benshi kurenza abantu babiri no guhagarika ingendo no gukora hanze kubisabwa.
Bitandukanye n'ingamba zabanje, izi mbogamizi zagiye zishyirwaho imbaraga na polisi binyuze mu gutanga ibihano no gutatanya abantu.
Ubucuruzi bwinshi bwahawe amabwiriza yo gufunga, uretse ubucuruzi bwitwa ko ari "ngenzi", harimo amaduka manini, ibicuruzwa by'imiti, amabanki, amaduka acuruza ibyuma, sitasiyo za lisansi n'amazu y'imodoka.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko arwaye COVID-19 yemejwe mu ntara ya Washington mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bw'inyanja ya Pasifika mu mugabo wari watashye avuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Igisirikare cya White House gishinzwe kurwanya Coronavirus cyashyizweho tariki ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko habaye ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'abaturage, kandi bushyiraho ingamba ku kwinjira kw'abagenzi baturutse mu Bushinwa.
