Nubwo Amerika yabigenje itangira kugerageza vuba, ibyo byibasiye ubukana bw'icyorezo icyo gihe.
Ibizamini byaranzwe n'ibikoresho by'ibizamini by'amakosa byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta ku bikoresho by'ibizamini bitari ibya leta (biva mu bigo by'imyitozo ngororamubiri, mu bigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare, no gushyiraho amahame agenga abantu bagombaga gupimwa kugeza mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe (gusabwa kwa muganga byasabwe nyuma yaho).
Kugeza ku itariki ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru cyitwa Washington Post cyatangaje ko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika hakozwe ibizamini bitarenga 4.000.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hatangijwe ibizamini bitarenga 14 000.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru Associated Press cyatangaje ko "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso kandi bakaba bari bafite ibyo muganga abasaba, bagombaga gutegereza amasaha cyangwa iminsi kugira ngo bakore ibizamini".
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, mu gice cya kabiri cya Werurwe amashuri yo mu gihugu cyose yari afunze. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zaburiwe ku byerekeranye n'ingaruka za coronavirus nshya ku gihugu n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo bo muri Imperial College y'i Londres.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo gutanga inkunga y'inyongera yo kwitegura no gusubiza coronavirus, ryatanze miliyari 8,3 z'amadolari mu nkunga y'ubutabazi ku bigo bya leta mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho ingamba zo gukumira ingendo ku bakozi, guhagarika inama, no gushishikariza abakozi gukora mu rugo.
Ibiganiro n'ibihe by'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari ingendo z'abantu benshi mu Burayi, ariko ko Ubwongereza butari mu byiciro by'ingenzi, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yaguye ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu cyose gifite ikibazo cy'ubukungu, bituma amafaranga ya leta agera ku rwego rwo gusubiza icyo kibazo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi bwafunze cyangwa bugabanya amasaha yo gukora muri Amerika yose mu kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu ma leta yose 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko umujyi wa New York City wari ufite 10,700 by'abanduye Coronavirus, kurusha umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda abantu kugaragara ko ari byo byakorwaga, kuko imibare y'abanduye yagabanutse kuva ku minsi 2.0 igera ku minsi 4.7.
Kuva ku ya 28 Werurwe, habayeho abantu 32,308 bemejwe mu mujyi wa New York, abantu 672 bakaba barapfuye bazize virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko hari abantu benshi banduye Coronavirus kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Kuva ku ya 8 Mata, abantu 400,335 bemejwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu 12,841 bakaba barapfuye.
Nk'uko amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru abivuga, ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, Perezida Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku itariki ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort, bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1.000, bwashyize ubwato mu kirwa cya New York.
