Muri leta ya New York, abanduye barenze 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. White House yanenzwe kubera gupfobya iterabwoba no kugenzura ubutumwa mu gihe yategekaga abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza ibitabo n'amagambo rusange ajyanye na virusi mu biro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Kwemera muri rusange uburyo Trump yakemuye ikibazo cy'ihungabana byashyizwe mu majwi n'amashyaka.
Bamwe mu bayobozi n'abatangazamakuru bo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika banenze icyizere Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zifite mu kuzana ibikoresho by'ibanze, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ibanze, bivuye mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'ingendo z'indege ryakoreshejwe mu gupima no guhanura uburyo bwo gukwirakwiza, ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere 2020.
Hashingiwe ku makuru yo mu mwaka wa 2018 yatanzwe n'ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga ry'ingendo z'indege, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo bihugu byabonye ingendo nyinshi zivuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe nk'ahantu hakunzwe cyane ku bantu bavuye i Wuhan.
Bali yagaragaye ko ari yo ifite ubushobozi buke mu bihugu 20 byakunzwe cyane mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yagaragaye ko ifite ubushobozi bwinshi.
Yavuze ko hari byinshi bigomba kumenyekana kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashimangira kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu gisubizo cyayo cy'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, mu gihugu cya Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habayeho ikibazo cy'umutekano w'ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ko imodoka z'abantu bose zashyiriweho guma mu rugo mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gukura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri ako karere, mbere na mbere binyuze mu ndege z'igihugu cy'iwabo, nyuma yo kurekurwa n'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Tayilande ni bamwe mu ba mbere mu gutegura ko abaturage babo bava muri icyo gihugu.
Pakisitani yavuze ko itazasubiza abaturage bayo bose bavuye mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Brazil yakuye Abanyakoreziya 34 cyangwa abagize umuryango wabo, usibye Abanyapolonye bane, Umunyashinwa umwe n'Umuhindi umwe.
