Abategetsi ba Australia bafashe abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 Gashyantare, babajyana mu kigo cya Christmas Island, nyuma yaho cyaje kongera gukoreshwa nk'ikigo cyo gushyira abantu mu kato, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Indege yo gukuraho abaturage ba Nouvelle Zélande yageze i Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Australia na Pacific) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cy'abasirikare mu mazi i Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zizavana Abanyamerika mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
