Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, leta y'Ubuhinde yatangiye gukura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari yaraguzwe na leta y'Afurika y'Epfo yasubije muri icyo gihugu abaturage 112 b'Afurika y'Epfo.
Iperereza ry'abaganga ryakorewe mbere y'uko batwara abantu, kandi abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basigaye inyuma kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyarwanda bageragejwe gusa ni bo basubijwe mu gihugu cyabo.
