Interaksyon yatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Philippines ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapore yatangaje ko izohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje impano ya miliyoni 18 z'intoki z'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi harimo n'imyenda y'ubwirinzi ibihumbi 10, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zitanga toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, kandi zasezeranya izindi miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu nkunga y'imari ku bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'uko abarwayi mu Bushinwa bagarutse, iki gihugu cyakomeje kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu bitandukanye byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke zo gufasha Ubutaliyani mu gucunga icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje imfashanyo za miliyoni 1.1 z'ibikoresho byo gupima, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60 000 yo kurinda umubiri i Addis Abeba muri Ethiopia kugira ngo bijye bitangwa n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bwa Afurika.
Nyuma yaho, yohereje ibikoresho 5,000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho bitanu byo guhumeka mu gihugu cya Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze imfashanyo z'imiti muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Czech byatangaje impungenge ku masike n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye ibikoresho 58,000 byo gupima virusi ya corona byakozwe n'Ubushinwa bifite igipimo cy'ubwiringiro cya 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwashubije udupfukamunwa 600,000 twari dufite inenge.
Ububiligi bwakusanyije udupfukamunwa 100.000 tutakiri mu bubiko, twavugwaga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'Ubushinwa bwakiriwe neza mu bice bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubutabazi by'ubutabazi mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga z'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa mu gucunga no gukumira icyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cya 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga ko bataye amakuru yatumye gukumira no gukumira bigorana, n'ikibazo cya none, aho leta nkuru "yatangaga amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo yirinde ubwoba buzabaho mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'icyunamo".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'abayobozi bakuru cyo gushyiraho itegeko ryo guhagarika ingendo muri Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko "nta gushidikanya ko atari inama ya OMS" kandi ko ari "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cy'umurava wo gukumira icyorezo mu karere cyagaragaye cyane". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemezwa kw'ikwirakwizwa hagati y'abantu hanze y'Ubushinwa no kwiyongera kw'imibare y'abandura mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icy'ubutabazi mpuzamahanga (PHEIC), cyaba icya gatandatu kuva icyo cyorezo cyatangira gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cya 2009.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom yavuze ko PHEIC yasabwe kubera "akaga ko gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bikennye n'ibifite umushahara wo hagati, bidafite sisitemu z'ubuzima zikomeye.
Mu gusubiza ku ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'imihango yo kugabanya ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho ingamba zo kubangamira ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "WHO idashishikariza abantu kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira gahunda yo gutegura ibihugu bikennye n'ibiciriritse, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gufasha ibihugu "bifite uburyo bwo kugenzura abantu banduye virusi, ndetse n'iyo yaba yongeye kwaduka".
Tedros yavuze ko "dukomeye cyane nk'aho ari twe dufitanye isano nke" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "gushora imari ubu cyangwa uzishyura nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'indwara.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, António Guterres, yemeye gutanga "ububasha bw'umuryango w'Abibumbye wose mu gisubizo".
Itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'iki cyorezo ryashyizweho, bituma rishobora guhuza ibisubizo byose by'umuryango w'abibumbye, WHO ivuga ko bizatuma "bashyira imbaraga mu kwivuza mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora kuzana ubunararibonye mu bijyanye n'imibereho myiza, ubukungu n'iterambere byatewe n'iki cyorezo".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abakozi ba OMS bahuje Ubushinwa ryahawe ubushobozi bwo guha impuguke mpuzamahanga na OMS ku butaka mu Bushinwa ubufasha mu gucunga uburwayi mu gihugu no gusuzuma "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'indwara" binyuze mu myitozo n'inama n'inzego zikomeye ku rwego rw'igihugu no gukora ingendo zo mu murima kugira ngo barebe "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'utugari, harimo n'imiterere y'imijyi n'icyaro". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi ikwiye gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya Coronavirus", ivuga ko nubwo ari kare cyane gutangaza icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba gushyiraho "icyiciro cyo kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo kiri gukwirakwira muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abafatanyabikorwa kugira ngo barebe uko ibintu bimeze. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko igipimo cy'ibyago bya Coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi kizazamurwa kiva kuri "cyinshi" kigashyirwa kuri "cyinshi cyane", ari na cyo kigero cyo hejuru cyo kuburira no gusuzuma ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'ubuvuzi ry'ibihe bidasanzwe, yatanze umuburo agira ati "iyi ni imvugo y'ukuri kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: Nimukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi mugomba kwitegura", ashimangira ko ingamba zo gusubiza neza zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu atemerera abayobozi b'ubuzima rusange gutangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza icyorezo ku isi byumvikanisha ko "turimo kwemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azashyirwa mu kaga k'iyi virusi".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS yari "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ibipimo biteye ubwoba by'ikwirakwira n'uburemere, n'ibipimo biteye ubwoba byo kutagira icyo ikora". OMS yahuye n'ibitekerezo byinshi ku byo byabonetse nk'ubuyobozi bubi bw'icyorezo, harimo gutangaza hakiri kare ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi muri pandemic.
Igisubizo cy'icyo kibazo cyagarutsweho n'ibisabwaga ku muyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, kugira ngo atangaze ko yeguye, byasinywe n'abantu 733.000 ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu za ONU zibarirwa mu icumi zashimangiye kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa buri muntu wese mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryatangaje ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo kugira icyo akora kugira ngo akize ubuzima bwe kandi ko leta ari yo ifite inshingano.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa gahunda y'ubuzima bitagomba na rimwe kuba urwitwazo rwo gutandukanya itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abantu b'abafite ubumuga buke, abageze mu za bukuru, abafite ibibazo byo mu mutwe, abatagira aho baba, abafite ubukene bukabije, abafunzwe, impunzi n'andi matsinda atazwi akeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ishinzwe ubutegetsi iri kuganira ku ngaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage ziterwa n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'i Burayi, OEC, ryatangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru agezweho kandi arambuye ku bisubizo by'amategeko mu bihugu byo hirya no hino ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Uhereye ku politiki yo gukomeza sisitemu z'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi yose kugeza ku ngaruka zo gufunga no gukumira ingendo, ikigo cya digitale kirimo ikigo cya Country Policy Tracker gifasha ibihugu kwiga ku bindi no korohereza igisubizo cy'isi yose ku kibazo cya Coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Abaminisitiri w'u Bwongereza, Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil, Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro kubera uburyo yayoboye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei yo mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi bo ku rwego rw'intara b'ishyaka rya gikomunisti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe kubera uburyo bakiriye ibikorwa byo gushyira abantu mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, ikimenyetso cy'uko abategetsi b'icyo gihugu batishimiye uko bakiriye iki cyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bemeza ko iki gikorwa cyakozwe mu rwego rwo kurinda Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Abashinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian banze kwemera mbere y'igihe icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira ibitekerezo by'ubugambanyi kuri COVID-19 byaturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bwa Donald Trump bwise Coronavirus "Virusi y'Abashinwa" cyangwa "Virus ya Wuhan" buvuga ko icengezamatwara ry'Ubushinwa "ryongereye virusi ubu yabaye icyorezo cyugarije isi yose", icyo kikaba cyarahamijwe na bamwe mu banenga ko ari ivangura ry'amoko n'uburyo bwo kugoreka ubuyobozi mu kurwanya indwara.
Daily Beast yabonye uburyo buhagije bwo gutangaza amakuru y'ibanze y'umukozi wa leta ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, mu nama y'umutekano w'igihugu, aho bavuga ko "ibi byose bifitanye isano n'u Bushinwa.
Twahawe inama yo kugerageza no kubona ubwo butumwa mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose, harimo ibiganiro n'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo. "Ibitangazamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byerekanye ko imihati y'Ubushinwa yo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bigize propagande yo kugira ingaruka ku isi.
Umuyobozi w'ibikorwa by'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi, Josep Borrell, yaburiye ko hari "ingingo ya politiki igizwe n'urugamba rwo kugira uruhare binyuze mu buryo bw'ibitekerezo by'ubwikunde n' 'ingamba z'ubuntu'.
Borrell yavuze kandi ko "Ubushinwa burimo gukwirakwiza ubutumwa bw'uko, bitandukanye na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, ari umufasha w'inshingano kandi wizewe".
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika guhagarika ibihano byayo kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, mu gihe byemezwa ko bwari butumye imfashanyo kuri ibyo bihugu.
Impano ya Jack Ma y'amasaga 100.000 yagenewe Cuba yahagaritswe n'ibihano bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika kandi bashinjwa ko bayobya inkunga yo mu bindi bihugu ikajya mu gihugu cyabo.
Kandi wumvise impaka zivuga ku myambaro z'ibumoso zivugwa mu bindi bihugu, urugero nk'u Budage, Otirishiya n'u Busuwisi; Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe amafunguro abarirwa mu magana yari ajyanye muri Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi udashyigikiye abahuye na Coronavirus mu Butaliyani.
Maurizio Massari, Ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa bwonyine ari bwo bwitabiriye ku mpande zombi.
Nta gushidikanya, icyo si ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'i Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ijambo rya telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'Uburusiya Vladimir Putin yateguriye ingabo z'Uburusiya kohereza abaganga ba gisirikare, imodoka zihariye zo guhanagura indwara, n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo y'umuntu utazwi mu rwego rwo hejuru mu rwego rwa politiki, avuga ko 80 ku ijana by'ibyo Uburusiya bwatanze "bitaga ku cyo byari bimaze cyangwa bitari bikenewe mu Butaliyani".
Uwo muyobozi yashinje u Burusiya gutangira igikorwa cy'igitero "cy'ubutaka n'ububanyi n'amahanga".
Perezida w'akarere ka Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubutaliyani, Luigi Di Maio, baretse amakuru y'itangazamakuru maze bagaragaza ko bishimiye cyane.
Uburusiya kandi bwohereje indege y'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "mu gutanga ubufasha ku bagenzi be b'Abanyamerika, [Putin] atekereza ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bo muri Amerika bari mu bihe byiza, na bo bari kugira icyo bakora mu buryo buhuje n'ibyo bakeneye".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO "Defender 2020" iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye n'ibihugu bya Baltique, imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO ikomeye cyane kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye, izakomeza ku kigero gito.
Umunyamabanga mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye uharanira kurwanya intwaro za kirimbuzi, Kate Hudson, yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati: "Muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange, ibi ntibikunda gushyira mu kaga ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika n'ibihugu bitandukanye by'i Burayi birimo, ahubwo bikanabangamira ubuzima bw'abaturage bo mu bihugu bakoreramo".
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye ibaruwa rusange abayobozi b'isi asaba ubufasha ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, avuga ko igihugu cye kigorwa no kurwanya iki cyorezo kubera kubura uburyo bwo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano bya Amerika kuri Iran. Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika ifata politiki rusange mu rwego rw'imibereho myiza mu bindi bihugu byateye imbere, harimo kwita ku buzima busanzwe, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango gihemba, n'amafaranga menshi yo gushyigikira ubuzima rusange.
Abasesenguzi mu bya politiki bari biteze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku mahirwe ya Donald Trump yo kongera gutorwa nk'umukuru w'igihugu mu matora ya 2020.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze ingamba z'ubwirakabiri n'iz'ubwigenge z'u Buyapani zo gushyira abantu mu kato, nyuma y'aho u Buyapani butangaje ko umuntu wese uza ava muri Koreya y'Epfo azashyirwa mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce twashyizweho na leta.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo mu mizo ya mbere wari warashyize ibice ku bisubizo Perezida Moon Jae-in yatanze kuri icyo kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon yahagarikwa ku mpamvu z'uko batitaga ku buryo bwiza bwo gucunga iki cyorezo, cyangwa se bashima uko yabyitwayemo. Icyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byemerera amategeko y'ubutabazi nk'igisubizo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuze ko ibyo bishobora gutuma ubutegetsi bukomeza ububasha bwabwo.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yemeye ko Minisitiri w'Intebe, Viktor Orbán, ashobora gutegeka ku mugaragaro, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko ndetse n'amatora no guhana abafatwa nk'abatanze amakuru y'ibinyoma kuri virusi n'uburyo leta ikemura ikibazo.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyateje ibibazo byinshi by'ibura ry'ibikoresho, bitewe no gukoresha ibikoresho byinshi mu kurwanya icyorezo, kugura ibintu mu buryo bwo guhungabana, no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze imiburo ku kibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'ikoreshwa ry'imiti ryongerewe ndetse n'ibihagarikwa by'ababikora.
Mu bice bitandukanye, habaye ibikorwa byo guhaha mu buryo bw'iterabwoba, byatumye ku mashuka y'ibikoresho by'ibanze harimo ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku, amazi mu mazi ya zacupa, ndetse n'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ibanze by'ibikoresho by'ibanze.
Uruganda rw'ikoranabuhanga mu buryo bwihariye rwatangiye kuburira ku gutinda kw'ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki.
Dukurikije uko umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom abivuga, icyifuzo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda kirakomeje incuro 100.
Ibi byatumye ibiciro byiyongeraho inshuro zigera kuri makumyabiri z'ibiciro bisanzwe kandi byanazamuye igihe cyo gutanga ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu mezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
Ibi kandi byateje ubukene bw'ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku isi hose, aho OMS yaburiye ko ibyo byashyiraga ubuzima bw'abakozi mu kaga.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatanze amahirwe mashya ku bagura b'Abashinwa, daigola, kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Uyu mushinga watumye habaho ibura ry'amafunguro y'abana mu masoko amwe n'amwe, nyuma yaho wahagaritswe na leta ya Ositaraliya. Nubwo hari umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, ndetse n'ibyifuzo by'ibiribwa by'abaturage, ibyo bice byombi byarahunze ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zafashwe n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ububiko butemewe n'amategeko n'ubucuruzi bw'ibikoresho by'ibanze zagize icyo zigeraho, bituma habaho inzara ikomeye y'ibiribwa yari yarahanuwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Amajyaruguru y'u Butaliyani afite umusaruro munini w'ubuhinzi ntiyabonye igabanuka rinini, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera nk'uko abahagarariye inganda babivuga.
Amashuka y'ibiribwa abura abantu yabonetse by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, kandi abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa batanze ibigega by'inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyokurya bihagije.
Amategeko nk'ayo arahari mu Butaliyani, asaba abahinzi b'ibiribwa kubika amafaranga mu gihe habaye ibyo bibazo.
Ibyangiritse ku bukungu bw'isi byumvikanywe mu Bushinwa: nk'uko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku ya 16 Werurwe, ubukungu mu Bushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba zafashwe na leta zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'ibicuruzwa byagabanutseho 20,5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari igihugu gifite ubukungu bunini n'ikigo cy'inganda, iki cyorezo cyafashwe nk'ikibazo gikomeye cy'ihungabana ry'ubukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu rwego rw'ubutasi rwa The Economist yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhungabana kugeza igihe habonetse ishusho isobanutse y'ibishobora kuzagaragara.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bashakashatsi bavuze ko ingaruka z'icyorezo ku bukungu ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kurenga icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Impuguke imwe yo muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis yagaragaje ko ingaruka z'amadolari miriyari 300 ku muyoboro w'ibikoresho ku isi zishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Ishyirahamwe ry'Ibihugu Bitanga Peteroli (OPEC) ryagaragaye ko "ryadohotse" nyuma y'ikunyuka k'ibiciro bya peteroli kubera ko Ubushinwa bwari bufite ibisabwa bike.
Amasoko y'imigabane ku isi yose yagabanutse ku ya 24 Gashyantare kubera ubwiyongere bukabije bw'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge zikomeje kwiyongera ku cyorezo cya Coronavirus, ibipimo bitandukanye by'isoko ry'imari muri Amerika birimo NASDAQ-100, S&P 500, na Dow Jones Industrial Average byagaragaje ibyigaragambyo bikomeye cyane kuva mu 2008, aho Dow yagabanutseho amanota 1,191, ari na yo yonyine yagabanutse cyane kuva mu bihe by'ihungabana ry'imari ryo mu 2007-08.
Indi indi indi indi indi indi indi yose yarangije icyumweru iri hasi y'ibice birenga 10%.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje ko ifite igipimo cy'ubudehe bw'u Bushinwa ariko ikomeza kubona ko nta gaciro ifite.
Agaciro k'ibicuruzwa kagiye gusubira hasi kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus, ku munsi wa 16 Werurwe ni bwo hagabanyutse cyane.
Hari benshi batekereza ko ari ihungabana ry'ubukungu rishobora kubaho.
