Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gusukura intoki), nanone bizwi nka "hygiène des mains", ni igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rwo gukuraho umwanda, ibinure, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu udashaka.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune buri gihe mu "bihe bikomeye" mu gihe cy'umunsi, bibuza ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'ibicurane na kolera, zikwirakwizwa mu nzira y'amaraso.
Abantu bashobora kandi kwandura indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero nka grippe cyangwa umugera w'ibicurane, urugero, iyo badakarabye intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku kanwa (ni ukuvuga mu maso).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa harimo: mbere na nyuma yo gusama, nyuma yo gusukura umwana cyangwa guhindura impapuro, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, na mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gufata inyama, inyama cyangwa amafi.
Niba nta mazi n'isabune biboneka, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje ivu.
Mbere yo gutegura ibyokurya, mu gihe cyo kubitegura no nyuma yaho.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Nyuma yo guhindura amagi cyangwa gukaraba umwana wakoresheje ubwiherero.
Nyuma yo gukorora, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ku biribwa cyangwa ku bintu by'inyamaswa byasigaye.
Isuku y'amaboko yerekeza ku bikorwa by'isuku bijyanye n'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa ubuvuzi bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki ni ukuzikuraho indwara ziterwa n'ibicurane (bakteriya, virusi, cyangwa izindi mikorobe zishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho bya shimi bishobora gutera uburwayi cyangwa kwangirika.
Ibyo ni iby'ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakoresha ibiribwa cyangwa abakora mu by'ubuvuzi, ariko ni na ko bimeze ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, coronavirus n'izindi ndwara zandura; gukumira indwara zandura ziterwa n'ibicurane; kugabanya ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
no kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa mu gihe cyo kubyara mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko kugira imyitwarire myiza yo gukaraba intoki bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu batera imbere mu buryo bworoheje.
Mu bihugu byateye imbere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazira indwara z'ibihaha n'iz'ubuhumekero ushobora kugabanywa binyuriye mu guhindura imyitwarire y'abana, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Icyo gikorwa cyoroshye gishobora kugabanya umubare w'abahitanwa n'iyo ndwara hafi 50%.
Gushyiraho ingamba zo gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya uburwayi bw'ibicurane ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, ibyo bikaba ari kimwe no kugeza amazi meza mu duce dukennye.
48% by'igabanuka ry'ibicurane bishobora kuba bifitanye isano no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda ibicurane n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (IRS), nk'uko bikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage hirya no hino ku isi.
Pneumonia, ni yo mpamvu y'ibanze ituma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu bapfa, ihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'ibicurane n'imyimba byose hamwe bihitana abana bagera kuri miriyoni 3,5 buri mwaka.
Dukurikije ibyavuzwe na UNICEF, guhindura gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero, bikaba ingeso isanzwe, bishobora gukiza abantu benshi kurusha inkingo cyangwa uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kuvura, bikagabanya impfu z'abarwaye diarrhée hafi icya kabiri, n'iz'abarwaye indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye ku kigero cya kimwe cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi bijyana n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku nk'igice cy'amahugurwa y'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki kandi birinda impetigo yandurira mu bantu iyo bakoranye imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Ingaruka mbi nke yo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutera ibikomere ku ruhu bitewe no gukama kw'uruhu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danimarike mu 2012 bwerekanye ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma uruhu ruba rufite ibisebe kandi rukagira uburakari, byitwa eczema cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, cyane cyane mu bakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi na byo byitwa ko ari kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara yo guhangayika cyane (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ingenzi mu kugabanya kwanduzanya indwara binyuze mu kanwa: nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (gusukura, guteka), nyuma yo gusukura umwana (kuhindura imbunda), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, na mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorakora inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko itarayifashe.
Indi mimerere aho uburyo bukwiriye bwo gukaraba intoki bugomba gukoreshwa mu kwirinda kwanduza indwara, harimo mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igisebe cyangwa igikomere; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa gukaraba; nyuma yo gukora ku bintu by'inyamaswa cyangwa ku matungo; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, hari umubare muto w'abantu bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo, 38.7% by'imiryango yari ifite akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ari yo ifite igipimo cyo hejuru ku kigero cya 97%, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ziri hafi y'ikigereranyo ku kigero cya 77%, n'Ubushinwa bufite igipimo cyo hasi ku kigero cya 23%. Uburyo butandukanye bwo guhindura imyitwarire ubu buriho kugira ngo byongere kwemerwa ku myambarire yo gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu bihe by'ingenzi. Gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'itsinda ku bana bo mu mashuri mu bihe runaka by'umunsi ni ubundi buryo mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere bwo gushyiramo imikoreshereze yo gukaraba intoki mu bana.
"Gahunda y'Ubuzima bw'Ingenzi" yashyizweho n'Urwego rw'Uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa by'inganda mu rwego rwo guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Gucukura udukoko kabiri mu mwaka, hamwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune, no gusukura amenyo buri munsi hakoreshejwe fluorure, ni byo byibanze muri iyo gahunda y'igihugu.
