Umunsi ukurikiyeho, mu gihe cy'iminota 30 cyangwa irenga, ujye ukaraba intoki n'ibiganza, hagati y'intoki n'impande, kugeza igihe amazi, uduhu cyangwa umutobe wumye.
Ibiganza bigomba kandi gukaraba neza, bikanyukurwa n'ibiganza byombi. Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe umuti wo gukaraba intoki, cyane cyane iyo intoki zanduye mu maso.
Gukoresha izi nkingo byiganje kubera ko byoroshye kuzikoresha kandi bikora vuba ku mikorobe; ariko, ntibigomba gusimbura gukaraba intoki neza keretse gusa iyo habonetse isabune n'amazi.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yo gukaraba intoki irimo inzoga bishobora gutuma uruhu rukuma keretse hongeyeho imboga n'ibinyobwa bihumanya uruhu.
Ingaruka zo gukama kwa alubumu ishobora kugabanuka cyangwa ikurwaho binyuze mu kongeramo glycerine na/cyangwa ibindi bintu bihumanya.
Mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, imiti yo gukaraba intoki irimo inzoga irimo emolients yatumye uruhu rutera uburibwe n'umwotsi muke ugereranyije n'isabune cyangwa imiti yo gukaraba.
Indwara y'uruhu itera indwara yo kubihana, urticaria y'uruhu cyangwa se kuribwa cyane n'inzoga cyangwa ibindi bintu bikoreshwa mu gusukura intoki z'inzoga, ni ibintu bidakunze kubaho.
Kuba batagaragazaga uburakari bwo guturika kw'uruhu, byaje kuba byiza cyane ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune n'amazi.
N'ubwo ari ingirakamaro, imiti itari mu mazi ntiyakuraho imyanda ku biganza, ahubwo ikayisukura gusa.
Niyo mpamvu ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bidakoreshwa neza nk'amazi n'isabune mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, kuko indwara zikiri mu ntoki.
Uburyo bw'ibikoresho by'isuku bitagira inzoga bugarukira cyane ku bintu bikoreshwa n'uburyo bikoreshwa, kandi mu mateka yabyo, byaranze cyane inzoga n'ibikoresho by'isuku bikoreshwa n'inzoga.
Vuba aha, uburyo bukoresha benzalkonium chloride bwagaragaye ko bugira ingaruka zikomeza no gukwirakwira ku mikorobe nyuma yo kubishyira mu bikorwa, bitandukanye na alcohol, yagaragaye ko ifite imbaraga nke nyuma yo kubikoresha kenshi, bishoboka ko biterwa n'ingaruka z'ingaruka zikomeje kwiyongera ku ruhu.
Abantu benshi bo mu midugudu ikennye ntibashobora kugura isabune, ahubwo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ubutaka.
Ibiraka cyangwa ubutaka bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha amazi meza, ariko bishobora kuba nta ngaruka nziza bifite nko gukoresha isabune.
Hari impungenge ko iyo ubutaka cyangwa imirabyo byandujwe na mikorobe, indwara ishobora gukwirakwira aho kugabanuka.
Kimwe n'isabune, umukungugu na wo ni umuti wo guhanagura indwara, kubera ko iyo uhuye n'amazi uba ufite umuti wa alkaline.
OMS isaba ko umukungugu n'umusenyi byajya mu mwanya w'isabune mu gihe nta sabune ihari.
Uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki bwasabwe n'Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu kwirinda kwanduza indwara burimo intambwe zikurikira:
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Ni byiza ko umuntu atangira kunywa amazi ashyushye kuko imisarani ishobora kuba ihumanye, ariko ubushyuhe bw'amazi bwo ntibugaragarire aho.
Gukaraba intoki, kubisukisha isabune nyinshi, harimo n'inyuma y'intoki, hagati y'intoki n'amaboko.
Isabuni ikuraho udukoko twanduza indwara mu ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko abantu bakunda gukaraba intoki neza iyo bakoresheje isabune aho gukoresha amazi meza.
Fata iminota 20 nibura.
Gukaraba bituma habaho guhohoterwa, bigatuma udukoko dukomoka ku nganda dukurwa ku ruhu, kandi iyo ukomeje gukaraba, bikuraho ingwara nyinshi.
Jya ukaraba neza n'amazi.
Gukaraba mu kintu cy'ibikoresho bishobora kongera kwanduza intoki.
Gutakaza igitambaro cyangwa kugisiga ngo kimare.
Ibice bikunze kwirengagizwa cyane ni ikiganza cya mbere, intoki, hagati y'intoki n'amaboko.
Amagi y'ibishushanyo n'amavuta y'ibishushanyo byashushanyije bishobora kuba birimo mikorobe.
Akenshi, umuti wo gutukura intoki ni wo utanga inama yo gutukura intoki; uruhu rwumye rushobora gutera ibikomere ku ruhu bishobora kongera ibyago byo kwanduza.
Uburyo butandukanye bworoshye bushobora gukorwa kugirango byorohereze gukaraba intoki aho amazi n'isabune bitagera, urugero nko gusuka amazi mu galasi cyangwa ku isima ifite imyobo ikwiye no/cyangwa gukoresha umwotsi iyo bibaye ngombwa mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Mu mimerere aho amazi atangwa ari make (nk'amashuri cyangwa uturere two mu byaro mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari uburyo bwo kubika amazi, nk' "ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi" n'ubundi buryo buhendutse.
Imashini ikoresha amazi mu buryo bw'amaboko ni ikoranabuhanga ryoroheje rikoresha urwabya rufungishijwe umugozi, n'umugozi ukoreshwa n'ibirenge kugira ngo usuke amazi make mu biganza byawe hamwe n'umuti w'isabune.
Kumesa intoki neza ni igice cy'ingenzi mu gikorwa cyo gusukura intoki, ariko hari impaka ku buryo bwiza bwo kumesa mu byumba bya rubanda.
Ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera bugaragaza ko impapuro z'isuku ari zo zisigaye ari nziza cyane kurusha imashini z'amashanyarazi zo kumesa intoki ziboneka mu byumba byinshi by'ubwiherero.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster, mu mujyi wa Londres, kandi buhagarariwe n'inganda z'impapuro z'umwenda, European Tissue Symposium, kugira ngo bagereranye urwego rw'isuku rwatanzwe n'impapuro z'umwenda, imashini zimesa intoki zishyushye n'imashini zimesa intoki zigezweho z'umuyaga.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki mu gikomoro cy'umwuka ushyuha, umubare w'ibinyabutabire byose wabonetse ku kigereranyo cya 194 ku ijana mu gice cy'ikiganza kiri hafi y'intoki na 254 ku ijana mu gice cy'iganza gisigaye.
Kumesa mu bikoresho byo kumesa umwuka byatumye umubare w'udukoko twanduye wiyongeraho 42% ku kigero mu gice cy'ikiganza kiri hafi y'intoki, n'ibikabije 15% mu gice cy'iganza kiri hasi.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki hakoreshejwe impapuro z'isuku, umubare wose w'udukoko wagabanyutse ku kigero cya 76% mu gice cy'ikiganza kiri hafi y'intoki no ku kigero cya 77% mu gice gisigaye cy'ikiganza. Abashakashatsi bakoze kandi ibizamini kugira ngo bamenye niba hari ubushobozi bwo kwanduza hagati y'abandi bakoresha n'aho bakoresha mu bwiherero bitewe n'uburyo bw'umwuma buri.
Ikigo cyo kumesa cy'umwuka, gitera umwuka hanze y'icyumba ku muvuduko wagaragajwe wa 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), cyabashije kwirukana mikorobe mu biganza no mu cyumba, bishobora kwanduza abandi bakoresha icyumba cy'ubwiherero n'ahandi hantu ku metero 2.
Gukoresha umwuma w'amaboko ushyushye byandurira mikorobe muri metero 0.25 z'umwuma.
Impapuro z'ibisate ntizigaragaza ikwirakwira ry'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze. Mu mwaka wa 2005 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt na Umwelt, uburyo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki bwasuzumwe.
Impinduka zikurikira mu mibare y'ibinyabutabire nyuma yo gukaraba intoki zabonetse:
Hariho abahanga benshi mu gukora imashini zo kumesa intoki, kandi imashini zo kumesa intoki zagereranyijwe no kumesa impapuro z'umwenda.
Gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe udusenda tw'amaboko twumye ni ubundi buryo bwo kwirinda kubura isabune n'amazi mu gihe uri mu rugendo.
Ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bifite inzoga bigomba kuba bifite nibura inzoga zingana na 60%.
Gukaraba intoki mu bitaro byabaye itegeko nyuma y'igihe kirekire umuganga w'Umuhungari Ignaz Semmelweis avumbuye ko ari ingirakamaro (mu 1846) mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bitanga ibitekerezo byo kwibutsa abakozi bo mu bitaro gukaraba intoki iyo bibukije.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abandura wagabanutse bitewe n'uko bakoreshaga imiti.
Gukaraba intoki mu bitaro ni ugufata iminota 15 gusa, ukoresheje isabune nyinshi n'amazi cyangwa gel yo gusukura no gukaraba intoki zose.
Ibiganza bigomba gukoreshwa mu gihe intoki ziri kumwe.
Niba hari ibisigazwa munsi y'amano, hakoreshwa umufuka wo kubikuraho.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuguma mu mazi ari ku biganza, ni ngombwa ko ukaraba neza kandi ukayomesha igitambaro gitunganye.
Nyuma yo kumesa, impapuro z'umwenda zigomba gukoreshwa mu gufunga amazi (no gufungura urugi niba ari ngombwa).
Ibyo bituma intoki zitongera kwandura izo mpanga.
Intego yo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi ni ukuvanaho udukoko dutera indwara ("udukoko") no kwirinda ko twanduzwa.
Ikinyamakuru cyitwa New England Journal of Medicine kivuga ko mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, abantu batigeze bakaraba intoki, kubera ko abaganga n'abaforomo benshi bakomeza kwibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bityo bakabatera mikorobe.
Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko gukaraba intoki neza n'ibindi bikorwa byoroheje bishobora kugabanya ubwandu bwo mu maraso bufitanye isano n'amabara ku kigero cya 66%.
Inyandiko y'amabwiriza y'umuryango ku isuku y'amaboko nayo ishobora kuboneka kuri uru rubuga kugira ngo ushyireho ibitekerezo.
Isubiramo rikwiye ryakozwe na Whitby et al.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi birashobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'amaboko, niba kwerekana ko hubahirijwe amategeko bisabwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryashyizeho "Ibihe bitanu" byo gukaraba intoki:
Nyuma yo gushyirwa mu mazi y'umubiri/amaraso
mbere yo gukora umurimo wo kwicisha bugufi,
Nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi, kongeramo imiti ya antiseptika mu isabune (sabune "y'imiti" cyangwa "irwanya mikorobe") bituma umuti wo gukaraba intoki ugira imbaraga zo kuzimya.
Kugira ngo "gusukura" intoki mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi bisaba kuba ufite akuma gashobora gufunguka no gufunga udakoresheje intoki, imiti imwe n'imwe yo kurwanya indwara ya chlorhexidine cyangwa iyodine, utwo gushyushya intoki mu gihe umaze gukaraba, n'agasaho k'intoki gatunganyijwe n'ibikoresho by'isuku bitunganyijwe kugira ngo usukure munsi y'imisumari.
Ibishushanyo byose bigomba kuvanwaho.
Iyi myitozo isaba gukaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku nkokora, akenshi mu minota 2-6 .
Igihe kirekire cyo gusukura (iminota 10) ntikigikenewe.
Mu gihe cyo gukaraba, amazi ari mu biganza ntiyagombye gutemba.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, intoki ziruma n'igihumyo cyanduye, hanyuma imyambaro y'ubuvuzi ikambikwa.
Kugira ngo udukoko dutera indwara tudahita twanduza abandi, ni byiza ko umuntu akaraba intoki cyangwa agakoresha umuti wo kuzirinda mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Ku bijyanye no kugenzura indwara z'ubwandu bw'ibicurane mu bitaro, byabonetse ko hari inyungu nyinshi yo gusukura intoki mu gihe cy'ibyumweru 20 bya mbere byo gusukura intoki, kandi hari n'inyungu idasanzwe y'inyongera yabonetse igihe umubare w'intoki zasukwaga warengaga 35%.
Gukaraba n'isabune isanzwe birenze inshuro eshatu igipimo cy'indwara zandura za bagiteri zanduzwa n'ibiribwa ugereranyije no gukaraba n'isabune irwanya bagiteri. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe umuti urimo inzoga n'ukunywa isabune irwanya bagiteri mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 kuri buri kimwe byagaragaje ko isuku y'intoki ikoreshwa na alcohol yagabanyije ubwandu bwa bagiteri ku kigero cya 26% kurusha isabune irwanya bagiteri.
Ariko, isabune n'amazi ni ingirakamaro kurusha imiti yo gukaraba intoki ikoreshwa mu gusukura intoki mu kugabanya virusi ya grippe A, H1N1, na Clostridium difficile mu ntoki.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwimbitse ku buryo bwo kuvura bw'uburyo bwiza kurusha ubundi mu bigo bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune bifatwa nk'igikoresho cy'ingenzi kandi cy'ingirakamaro mu by'ubukungu kugira ngo umuntu agire ubuzima bwiza ndetse n'imirire myiza kurushaho.
Ariko kandi, kutagira amazi yizewe, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo z'abantu, mu mashuri no mu mirimo, bituma kugera ku muco w'isi yose wo gukaraba intoki bitoroha.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro cya Afurika, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki hafi y'ubwiherero bwa leta cyangwa bwigenga ni bike, n'ubwo hari uburyo bworoshye bwo kubaka aho bakaraba intoki.
Icyakora, kudahanagura intoki bishobora kuba ari ingaruka z'ingeso zashinze imizi aho kuba ingaruka z'ibura ry'isabune n'amazi.
Gushishikariza no kuvuganira gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ya politiki, bigatuma abantu bamenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki, kandi bigatuma abantu bahindura imyitwarire yabo mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bikore neza, bisaba ko hakorwa igenzura no gusuzuma.
Isuzuma ry'ubushakashatsi 70 ryagaragaje ko uburyo bushingiye ku baturage ari bwo bw'ingirakamaro mu kongera gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikennye n'ibiciriritse, mu gihe gahunda zo kwamamaza ku bantu ari zo zidakora neza. Urugero rwo guteza imbere gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "Inzira y'inyenyeri eshatu" ya UNICEF ishishikariza amashuri gushyiraho ingamba zoroshye kandi ziciriritse zo kwemeza ko abanyeshuri bakaraba intoki n'isabune, mu bindi bisabwa n'isuku.
Iyo urebye neza, amashuri ashobora kuva ku nyenyeri imwe agera ku nyenyeri eshatu.
Kubaka ahantu ho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo kwamamaza gukaraba intoki bigamije kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi Mpuzamahanga wo Gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bugamije guhindura imyitwarire.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwarebye ingaruka z'amafaranga yose yo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere ku bijyanye no kugenzura DALY.
Ariko kandi, ubushakashatsi bumwe bugaragaza ko guteza imbere gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari byo bigira inyungu nyinshi kurusha ibindi bikorwa by'amazi n'isuku.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu  cyane cyane ku bantu bari mu mimerere igoranye nk'ababyeyi baherutse kubyara cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro  katangajwe bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 hagati n'abantu babiri batangije isuku y'intoki: umuganga w'Umuhungari witwa Ignaz Semmelweis wakoraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya, na Florence Nightingale, Umwongereza "washinze ubuvuzi bwa none".
Icyo gihe, abantu bari bagikeka ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi zitwa miasmas.
Mu myaka ya za 80, indwara ziterwa n'ibyokurya hamwe n'ubwandu bufatika mu buvuzi byatumye ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitera inkunga cyane abantu kugira isuku y'amaboko nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye mu bihugu byinshi abantu barushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda indwara zandura.
Urugero, ibyapa byanditseho "uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki mu buryo bukwiriye" byashyizwe iruhande rw'ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu byumba bya rubanda no mu byumba by'ubwubatsi bw'ibiro by'ibiro n'ibibuga by'indege mu Budage.
Imvugo ngo "gukaraba intoki" isobanura kwatura ko udashaka kwemera inshingano cyangwa kwemera ikintu runaka.
Ryaturutse mu murongo wa Bibiliya wa Matayo, aho Ponsiyo Pilato yakarabye ibiganza bye ku cyemezo cyo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko ryahindutse imvugo ikoreshwa cyane mu moko amwe n'amwe y'Abongereza.
Muri Macbeth ya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki ku gahato mu kugerageza gukaraba ikizinga cy'indoto, agaragaza umutimanama we umujinya ku byaha yakoze kandi yatumye umugabo we akora.
Byongeye kandi, byagaragaye ko abantu, nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa kubona ibikorwa bitemewe, bakunda gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, kandi bakunze guha agaciro ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bashobora gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kubona bene iyo foto, ntibashobora gukora ibindi bikorwa by'indishyi byo "kubanza gukora isuku", urugero nko gukora umurimo w'ubwitange.
Amadini ateganya gukaraba intoki kubw'impamvu z'isuku n'iz'ikimenyetso. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, ukoresheje amazi ariko si isabune, gukaraba intoki ni kimwe mu biranga umuhango wo gukaraba intoki mu madini menshi, harimo idini rya Bahá'í, idini ry'Abahindu, tevilah na netilat yadayim mu idini ry'Abayahudi, ubwiherero mu Bukristo, no kwiyuhagira mu idini rya Isilamu. Amadini kandi yerekana gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku, cyane cyane nyuma y'ibikorwa bimwe na bimwe.
Idini ry'Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abayisilamu ryemera ko umuntu akaraba intoki nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero.
Kandi idini ry'Abahindu, iry'Ababuda, iry'Abasiki n'iry'Abayisilamu ryemera ko umuntu akaraba intoki mbere yo kurya na nyuma yo kurya.
Igenzura ry'akaga mu kazi kuri COVID-19
Igenzura ry'ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19 ni ugushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi kugenzura ibyago byo kwirinda indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura ibyago mu kazi neza bishingiye ku kazi n'akazi ubwako, hashingiwe ku igenzura ry'ibyago by'ahantu umuntu yashoboraga kwandurira, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'impamvu z'ibyago ku bakozi ku giti cyabo bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'Urwego rw'Ubuzima n'Umutekano mu Mirimo (OSHA), imirimo ifite ibyago bike byo kwandura ifata umwanya muto mu kazi, aho usanga abantu n'abandi bakozi bakorana bagirwa inama yo kwirinda kwandura, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukomeza kwirinda umwuka no gukora isuku no gukiza indwara mu kazi.
Ibikorwa bifite ibyago byo kwandura birimo ibyo bisaba guhura kenshi cyangwa by'umwihariko guhura n'abantu batazwi ko banduye cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba banduye bitewe no kwanduza mu baturage cyangwa kuba bari mu ngendo hanze y'igihugu.
Ibyo bikubiyemo abakozi bakorana n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorera abantu benshi, no mu isoko rya ruganda rifite ibicuruzwa byinshi.
Mu byo abantu bo muri iki cyiciro bakenera kwirinda, harimo kwirinda indwara, guhumeka neza hakoreshejwe ibikoresho by'isuku bikora neza, gutwikira neza no kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umuntu ku giti cye mu gihe hagize umuntu wemezwa ko afite COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakora mu nzu z'ibiro by'abapfuye bahura n'abantu bafite COVID-19 yemewe cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, ibyo bikaba byongera ibyago byo kwandura cyane iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa ku bantu bafite COVID-19 yemewe cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite ubwandu bwa aerosol, kandi bagakoranya cyangwa bagakora ku bipimo by'abo bantu.
Ibipimo by'akaga bikwiye ku bakozi nk'abo birimo ibyuma by'ubwubatsi nk'ibyuma by'ubukana by'ubushyuhe n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bikwiye ku kazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kudakora kubera uburwayi, kubera ko bagomba kwita ku bandi, cyangwa se kubera gutinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Amategeko y'ubucuruzi ashobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibicuruzwa bikenewe ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubona ibyo bicuruzwa (nk'ubucuruzi bwo hanze y'amasaha y'ikiruhuko cyangwa ku nguzanyo cyangwa kuri drive-thru).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibikoresho mu turere twibasiwe cyane na COVID-19 bishobora guhagarikwa.
Amategeko avuga ku byiciro by'ibyago bifitanye isano n'aho bakorera imirimo itandukanye, harimo aho baturuka, ibyago bivuka mu ngo no mu baturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo nk'imyaka y'iza bukuru cyangwa uburwayi bw'igihe kirekire.
Nanone kandi, bashyiraho ingamba zo kurwanya izo ngaruka, n'ingamba zo guhangana n'ibibazo bishobora kuvuka bitewe n'ibyorezo.
Imyiteguro n'ingamba zo kurwanya indwara zandura zishobora gushyirwa mu nama z'igihugu cyangwa iz'akarere.
Intego zo kugira icyo umuntu akora mu gihe cy'icyorezo zirimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira ibibazo by'ubuzima, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bandi bantu mu byiciro by'ibicuruzwa.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho isosiyete iherereye, bugira ingaruka ku byo ikora.
Urutonde rw'ibyangombwa by'akaga ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu buzima n'umutekano mu kazi kugira ngo ibyangombwa by'akaga bishyirwe hamwe hakurikijwe uko bikora.
Iyo ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho, uburyo bwo kugenzura neza ni bwo butegurwa, hakurikiraho kugenzura mu rwego rw'ubuyobozi, hanyuma hakagenzurwa ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
Igenzura ryubwubatsi ririmo gukumira abakozi ku ngorane zijyanye n'akazi hatitawe ku myitwarire y'umukozi, kandi rishobora kuba igisubizo cy'ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'amafaranga menshi.
Igenzura ry'ubwubatsi ni impinduka mu politiki cyangwa mu mikorere y'akazi bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidashobora gukora neza kurusha inzego z'ubwubatsi n'iz'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu gukumira ibyangijwe.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku kaga ku mukozi, bugashyirwa mu buryo bukwiriye uko bikenewe (urugero nk'ibinyabutabire byo guhumeka), bukoreshwa mu buryo bukwiriye kandi buhoraho, bugasuzumwa buri gihe, bugakomeza kandi bushyirwa mu mwanya wacyo uko bikenewe, kandi bukurwaho, bukayisukura kandi bugashyingurwa cyangwa bugaseswa mu buryo bukwiriye kugira ngo birinde kwanduzwa.
Dukurikije Urwego rw'Ubuzima n'Umutekano mu Mwuga (OSHA) muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, imirimo ifite ibyago bike byo kwandura ifata umwanya muto mu kazi hamwe n'abandi bakozi bagenzi babo.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zisabwa ku kazi kose zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi mu buryo bwitondewe, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye no gukoresha umwambaro wo guhumeka, harimo no gufunga isesemi n'ubuhumekero, gutegura imifuka yo gukaraba no gukoramo imyanda isanzwe, gutegura gukora mu buryo bwa kure cyangwa gukora mu byiciro, niba ari ngombwa, kubuza gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi bakozi no gukomeza isuku no gusukura ibidukikije.
Kumenya vuba no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwandura ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bantu mu kazi.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cy'Amerika cyasabye abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bazaba batakigira umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso by'uburwayi nibura amasaha 24 nta miti ikoreshwa yo kugabanya umuriro cyangwa kugabanya ibindi bimenyetso, kandi cyasabye kandi ko politiki zo kuruhuka indwara zaba ziruhije, zemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kwita ku muntu urwaye wo mu muryango, kandi ko bagomba kumenya izo politiki.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, imirimo ifite ibyago byo kwandura by'inshuro nyinshi ikubiyemo imirimo isaba ko umuntu aba hafi y'ibirenge 6 cyangwa se ko aba hafi y'abantu bataramenyekana ko barwaye COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho kuyandura, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'uko abantu bahora bayanduza mu gace k'ikigo cyangwa bitewe n'uko umuntu aherutse kujya mu mahanga mu gihugu kirimo ubwandu bwinshi bwa COVID-19.
Ibi birimo abakozi bahuye n'abaturage muri rusange nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo abantu benshi, hamwe n'amaduka amwe n'amwe acuruza ibicuruzwa byinshi. Igenzura ry'ubwubatsi kuri iri tsinda n'amatsinda y'abari mu kaga gakomeye harimo kwinjiza imyuka ikora neza cyane, kongera umwuka, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nko gukoresha ibikoresho by'isuku bya plastiki, no gushyiraho idirishya rya gariyamoshi mu rwego rwo kwita ku bakiriya. Igenzura ry'ubuyobozi kuri iri tsinda n'amatsinda y'abari mu kaga gakomeye harimo gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo, gusimbuza amateraniro yo kuvugana imbonankubone, gushyiraho gahunda z'amahugurwa, guhagarika ibibazo bitari ngombwa kubera icyorezo cya COVID-19, guteza imbere gahunda z'itumanaho harimo no gutanga urubuga rw'ibanze rwo gusubiza abakozi, gutanga amabwiriza ku bijyanye n'isuku, gukoresha ibikoresho by'ibanze byo kurinda abakozi cyangwa gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi, gutanga amahugurwa ku bijyanye n'akazi, gushyira abakozi ku kazi, gutanga amabwiriza ku bijyanye n'ibikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho by'ibanze, kwirinda COVID-19, no kubungabunga umutekano w'abakozi n'abakozi n'abandi.
Abakozi bari muri iri tsinda ry'abafite ibyago bakunze gukenera imashini zifasha guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, uburyo bwiza bwo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bantu bari mu ndege harimo gutandukanya umuntu urwaye n'abandi bantu ku ntera ya metero 6, gushyiraho umukozi w'indege ukorera umuntu urwaye akamushyiraho agapfukamunwa, cyangwa gusaba umuntu urwaye ko apfuka umunwa n'umwembe we mu gihe ari gucokoza cyangwa gusama.
Abakozi bagomba kwambara utuntu tw'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi tw'igiceri igihe bakorera umurwayi cyangwa bakagira aho bahurira n'imyanda cyangwa uturere dushobora kwanduzwa, kandi wenda n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umuntu ku giti cye niba umurwayi afite umuriro, agakomeza gukorora cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Inkweto n'ibindi bintu by'igiciro kimwe bigomba kujugunywa mu isakoshi y'ibisigazwa by'ibinyabuzima biteje akaga, hanyuma imbuga zanduye zikagomba gusukurwa no gukorerwa isuku. Ku ngendo z'ubucuruzi, harimo amato y'ubwato n'andi mato arimo abagenzi, kugenzura akaga birimo gusubika urugendo rw'umunyeshuri urwaye, kwisanzura no kubwira abaganga bo mu ndege ako kanya niba hari umuntu ufite umuriro cyangwa indi ndwara mu gihe cy'urugendo.
Mu buryo bwiza, ku mashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC isaba ko hashyirwaho igihe gito cyo gusukura no guhanagura indwara mu gihe umuntu wafashwe n'iyo ndwara yaba yari mu nzu, hatitawe ku kuba virusi yarakwirakwiriye mu baturage.
Iyo hari ikwirakwira ry'abaturage rito cyangwa ryoroshye, uburyo bwo gutandukanya abantu bushobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa, nko guhagarika ingendo zo mu mirima, amakoraniro, n'andi matsinda manini nk'amasomo y'imyitozo ngororamubiri cyangwa amajwi, cyangwa amafunguro mu kabyiniro, kongera umwanya hagati y'ameza, amasaha yo kugera no kuva ku kazi, kugabanya abasura batari ngombwa, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho kwita ku buzima bw'abana bafite ibimenyetso by'ibicurane.
Iyo hari ikwirakwira ryinshi mu baturage, usibye ingamba zo kwirinda, abantu bashobora kureka ishuri igihe kirekire. Ku bategetsi bashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora imirimo ya buri munsi, ibyago by'ubuzima bwihuse bifatwa nk'ibito na CDC.
Biravugwa ko abapolisi bahuye n'abantu bakekwaho COVID-19 cyangwa bafite indwara yemewe bakurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'ubutabazi, harimo no gukoresha ibikoresho bikwiye byo kwirinda.
Niba hari aho umuntu yahuye n'umuntu mu gihe cyo gufata, abakozi bagomba gusukura no gusukura umwenda wabo n'ibindi bikoresho mbere yo kubikoresha bakoresheje umutobe usanzwe wo gusukura cyangwa igitambaro, kandi bagakurikiza amabwiriza asanzwe y'imikorere yo kubika no gushyira hanze PPE ikoreshwa no kubika no kumesa imyenda.
OSHA ibona ko abakozi bamwe na bamwe bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima n'abakora mu nzu z'abarwayi bari mu byiciro by'ibyago byo kurwara cyane cyangwa cyane.
Imirimo ifite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura harimo abageza imiti, abavura, abakora mu mavuriro n'abakora mu gutwara abarwayi, baba bagaragarijwe abarwayi bafite COVID-19 yemewe cyangwa bakekwaho.
Ibyago byo kwandura biba byinshi iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo gukora aerosol ku barwayi ba COVID-19 yemewe cyangwa bakekwaho, cyangwa bakusanya cyangwa bagakora ku bipimo by'abo barwayi.
Uburyo bwo gukora aerosol burimo gutwika, uburyo bwo gutera icyi, broncoscopy, uburyo bumwe na bumwe bwo gusuzuma amenyo cyangwa gutoragura ibipimo by'ibipimo.
Imirimo yo mu nzu y'ubuvuzi ifite ubukana bwinshi ikubiyemo abakozi bakora mu gutegura imibiri y'abantu bafite COVID-19 yemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho uburwayi mu gihe bapfuye; ibyago byo kwanduzwa bihinduka byinshi iyo bakoze autopsies.
Gutanga umwuka w'ingutu udasanzwe bishobora kuba byiza mu gihe cy'imibonano mpuzabitsina n'ubuvuzi.
Inyamaswa zigomba gufatwa mu buryo bwo kwirinda bw'icyiciro cya 3 cy'umutekano wa biochimique.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abarwayi binjira mu bitaro batandukanywa mu byumba bibiri bitandukanye byo gutegereza bitewe n'uko ari abantu bakekwaho COVID-19.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ibikoresho byo guhumeka mu maso bifite N95 byemewe na NIOSH cyangwa ibikoresho byo guhumeka by'ikirenga bigomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'umushinga w'ubwirinzi bwo guhumeka wanditse kandi urimo ibipimo, amahugurwa n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi.
Ubundi bwoko bw'ibikoresho byo guhumeka bushobora gutanga uburinzi no kunoza ihumure ry'umukozi. OMS ntishishikariza abantu kwambara imyenda kuko COVID-19 ari indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, kandi ntiyitambukira mu mazi yo mu mubiri atari mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
OMS isaba gusa ko abakozi bakora ibizamini ku kirindiro bajya mu bitaro bakoresha agapfukamunwa.
Ku bakora mu rwego rwo kuvura, kuvura cyangwa gutwara abarwayi ba COVID-19 badafite uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, OMS isaba ko umuntu yambara agapfukamunwa, indorerwamo cyangwa udukingirizo tw'amaso, umwambaro wo kubaga n'intoki.
Iyo habaye igikorwa cyo gukora aerosol, agapfukamunwa ka kirimbuzi gashyirwa mu cyuma cyo guhumeka cya N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko gutanga PPE ku isi hose bidahagije, OMS isaba ko hakorwa ibishoboka byose kugira ngo PPE ikoreshwe mu buryo bwa telemedicine, hagashyirwaho inzitizi z'umubiri nka Windows, byemerera gusa abita ku barwayi kwinjira mu cyumba kimwe n'umurwayi wa COVID-19, bakoresha PPE ikenewe gusa mu gikorwa runaka, bakoresha mu buryo buhoraho ibikoresho byo guhumeka bitavanwaho mu gihe bavura abarwayi benshi bafite iki kibazo kimwe, bagenzura kandi bagashyira hamwe gahunda yo gutanga PPE, kandi bakirinda abantu badafite ibimenyetso kwambara udupfukamunwa.
