Icyorezo cya COVID-19 ni ikintu cyerekana neza isano riri hagati y'abantu bose ku isi ndetse n'inshingano dufite ku bandi.
Ibibazo byabyo nta shingiro bifite, ariko tuzi ko ibikorwa byacu byiza cyane bituruka ku bwumvikane bw'isi yose, ubufatanye no kubaka umuryango, ari byo shingiro ry'uyu muryango.
Ubufatanye n'ubwitange twabonye mu bakozi bacu bose binyuze kuri email, guhamagara no kuganira ni igihamya gikomeye cy'abantu badasanzwe dufite amahirwe yo gukorana nabo.
Nshimishwa cyane kandi nishimira kuba mfite mwese nk'abakozi bagenzi banjye.
