Uyu muntu yanyibukije ko ari iby'ingenzi ko isi yose ishobora kubona Wikipedia muri iki gihe, kandi ko ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cy'uko iyi nkunga y'ingenzi ikomeza kuba kuri interineti kandi igakoreshwa na buri wese.
Akazi kanyu gatuma ibyo bishoboka, kuko mukomeza gukora, mukishyura abakozi bagenzi bacu, mukomeza umutekano w'abaturage bacu.
Isi ikeneye amakuru Wikipedia itanga kurusha ikindi gihe cyose.
Iki ni igihe aho atari ibyo dukora gusa, ahubwo n'uburyo tubikora, bizagira ingaruka zikomeye ku isi.
Kubera akamaro k'iki gikorwa n'uruhare rwawe muri cyo, tugiye kugira impinduka zikomeye mu buryo dukorana, guhera mu cyumweru gitaha.
Guhindura akazi n'amasaha yacu
Nk'uko Robyn yabitangaje mbere, itsinda rya C ryashyizwe hamwe mu ijoro ryakeye kugira ngo rigire icyo rivuga ku buryo tuzakoresha igihe cyacu n'amasaha tuzakoresha mu minsi n'amezi ari imbere.
Muri iyo nama, twasuzumye icyo tubona ari igikorwa gikwiriye ku byo turiho ubu n'uburyo bwiza bwo gukomeza umuteguro urambye muri icyo gihe.
Twifuza kugabanya imihangayiko no gushyigikira umurimo wacu mu gihe kirekire.
Niba ukeneye kumara igihe runaka utari mu rugo, nta kibazo.
Ku bakozi bose, ababaha serivisi n'abakozi bashinzwe amasezerano:
twiteze ko tuzakora amasaha 4 ku munsi, cyangwa amasaha 20 mu cyumweru, kugeza igihe tuzaba twahawe indi nshingano.
Ntituri gutangaza umunsi mukuru. Niba ushobora gukora amasaha asanzwe, ushobora kuba ingirakamaro ku murimo wacu.
Hagati aho, isi iri mu bihe bidashidikanywaho, kandi niba ukeneye kwita ku bo ukunda, kugura ibyokurya cyangwa kujya kwa muganga, imibereho yawe myiza ni yo ifite agaciro.
Ntiturimo gukurikirana amasaha yabo.
Niba urwaye, ntugire akazi.
Iryo tegeko ntiryagombaga no kuvugwa, ariko twafashe umwanzuro wo kuritangaza.
Nta cyangombwa cyangwa ikiruhuko cy'akazi gihemba gikenewe. gusa ujye ubwira umuyobozi wawe gufasha abakozi bawe gusubiramo igihe n'amasaha kugira ngo umenye ko ibice by'ingenzi by'akazi byitaweho.
(Niba usanganywe COVID-19, umenyeshe Bryan mu rwego rw'amahugurwa n'ibyangombwa kugira ngo urwego rwe rushobore kugufasha no kureba ko ikibazo cyawe cyahawe ubuyobozi bw'ikigo).
Abakozi bakora ku isaha bazajya bahembwa umushahara wose.
Twabivuze mbere, kandi twiyemeje kubahiriza amasezerano yacu ku ba rwiyemezamirimo bacu n'abakozi bacu bakora ku isaha.
Buri wese azahabwa umushahara we ashingiye ku nyandiko y'akazi asanzwe yakoze mu bihe bisanzwe.
Imishahara igenda itandukana niba urwaye kandi udashobora gukora.
Niba ushaka gukora, turagushyigikiye byimazeyo.
Abantu benshi babona ko akazi ari uburyo bwo guhangana n'imihangayiko bitewe n'imimerere iriho muri iyi si.
