Gusa turagusaba ko wabimenyesha umuyobozi wawe, kugira ngo tumenye icyo twakwitega maze dufashe ibikorwa byawe uko bikwiye.
Imirimo imwe n'imwe ifatwa nk'ibanze.
Hari ibikorwa tugomba gukomeza gukora.
Amatsinda y'ubwubatsi bw'urubuga, HR, Reliability & Security na Fundraising (mu bindi) akora ibikorwa by'ingenzi bishobora gukenera inkunga yinyongera.
Tuzatangira uburyo bwo gusuzuma intego zacu z'iki gihe, duhindure intego zacu kugira ngo dushyigikire ibyo dushinzwe.
Hari byinshi byo gukora kuri twese, kandi tuzajya twibanda ku mishinga y'ingenzi cyane.
Guhagarika vuba nta cyo bizatugezaho mu gihe kizaza.
Ntabwo tugiye "gukora cyane kugira ngo dusubirane igihe cyatakaye" icyorezo kirangiye.
Ntibizagusaba gukora amasaha y'ikirenga kugira ngo usohoze igihe ntarengwa ubu kidashoboka.
Twemeye ko imimerere yahindutse, kandi tuzakora ku buryo dushyiraho intego nshya n'igihe ntarengwa, uko bikwiye.
Bizagendekera bite gahunda y'umwaka?
Kugira ngo duhindure imimerere yacu nshya n'ibyo twiteze ku masaha akoreshwa ku munsi, twifuza guhindura igihe cyo gutanga gahunda yacu y'umwaka ya 2020-2021.
Intego yacu ni ugutanga ingamba zo kongera gahunda yacu ya 2019-2020, izatanga umwanya munini mu ngengo y'imari, kandi abakozi bashyire imbere imirimo y'ibanze, kwita ku bantu n'abo bakunda, mu gihe duhuza abakeneye cyangwa bashaka gukora mu minsi mike iri imbere.
Gutegura igihe bigabanya cyane akazi k'igenamigambi kariho ubu n'igitutu ku muryango wose.
Tuzatanga igitekerezo cyacu ku buyobozi mu cyumweru gitaha, kandi tuzatanga amakuru ku bayobozi n'abakozi ku ntambwe zikurikiraho mu gihe tuzaba tumaze kubona icyemezo.
Turashimira itsinda ry'Abadepite b'umwaka ku buyobozi bw'iki gikorwa.
Imimerere y'ibiro, uko byerekanwa n'isuku
Mu cyumweru gishize, twumvise ko umwe mu bakozi bacu bo muri San Francisco ashobora kuba yaranduye virusi ya COVID-19.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, mu rwego rwo kwirinda, twashyizeho itsinda ry'abakora isuku yo kwirinda virusi kugira ngo basukure imyanda yose iri ku biro byacu byo muri San Francisco.
Bakoresheje umuti wihariye wo kurwanya virusi mu bitaro kugira ngo basukure imyanda yose, ndetse n'inzu y'imbere n'ibyuma byose bitwara abantu bitwara abantu ku igorofa ryacu.
Inyubako iri gukoresha gahunda yayo yo kwita ku buzima bw'abantu ikoresheje ibikoresho bitagira ubwandu ku bayirimo.
Turishimye cyane kuba ibiro byacu bizaba byiteguye neza igihe tuzaba tugiye kugaruka.
Ibiro byacu i Washington biri mu kigo cya WeWork, cyakoranye na twe gahunda za COVID-19 hamwe n'abakozi bose b'i Washington.
Mu cyumweru gishize, ibiro byacu i Washington byahinduwe mu buryo bwa kure, mu buryo buhuje n'amabwiriza twahawe na San Francisco.
Nk'uko bamwe mu bo dufatanyije i New York bazi, turimo no kuganira ku bijyanye no gukodesha ibiro i Brooklyn.
Ibi biganiro biracyakomeje ariko bishobora gutinda.
Bamwe mu bo dukorana barimo gukora kure ku nshuro ya mbere.
Abo dukorana bamaze igihe kirekire bakorera kure bazi ko bishobora kuba ari uguhuza, kandi bifuza gutanga inama:
Mujye mugabanya igihe cy'amateraniro, mugategura isaha imwe cyangwa ebyiri gusa.
Niba ari ngombwa ko habaho ibyigwa birebire, tekereza kubigabanyamo iminsi myinshi.
Mujye mutegura iteraniro, mugire gahunda, kandi mujye mutanga inyandiko zo gusoma mbere y'igihe.
Koresha videwo nk'ibisanzwe, ukoresheje ibikoresho nka Google Docs na Zoom kugirango byorohereze abantu gukorana no guhuza mu gihe nyacyo.
Jya ugira umuyobozi wo koroshya amateraniro, umuntu wo kugenzura ibibazo byo mu kiganiro no ku rutonde rw'abagize uruhare, n'undi wo gufasha kwandika (cyangwa kwandika inyandiko z'ubufatanye).
Ohereza ubutumwa bugufi kuri tech support niba ukeneye udutambaro tw'amajwi tworoshye.
Mujye mukoresha amafaranga y'ubutabazi mu gihe cy'ibiza kugira ngo mugure ibyokurya byoroheje.
