Angiotensin converting enzyme type 2 (ECA2) ni enzyme ifata uruhu rw'inyuma (membrane z'ingirabuzimafatizo) z'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ECA2 ikuraho ibikorwa bya angiotensin converting enzyme (ECA) ifitanye isano no kugabanya angiotensin II no kuzamura Ang (1-7), bigatuma iba umuti wizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ECA2 ikora kandi nk'aho inzobere mu nsoro z'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe bwa coronavirusi.
