Angiotensin converting enzyme type 2 ni metaloenzyme irimo zinc iri ku butaka bw'umubiri w'umubiri n'izindi ngirabuzimafatizo.
Poroteyine ya ECA2 irimo urubuga rwa peptidase M2 rwa N-terminal n'urubuga rwa C-terminal rw'ibinyabutabire bya amino na colectrin mu byiciro by'impyiko.
ECA2 ni poroteyine yo mu bwoko bwa 1 y'uruhu rw'umwimerere, ifite urubuga rwayo rw'imikorere ya enzymatic rwigaragaza ku gipimo cy'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha no mu bindi binyabuzima.
