ECA2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ECA2 ifatanye na membrane y'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubuhumekero z'ubwoko bwa II, intanga ntoya, intanga z'amaraso n'iz'amaraso, n'ingingo z'imitsi y'amaraso mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
Ikoreshwa rya mRNA ya ECA2 riboneka no mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu mubiri, mu gice cy'imbere cy'ubwonko, no mu mutwe.
Inshingano y'ibanze ya ECA2 ni ugukora nk'igihombo cya ECA.
ECA ifata angiotensin yo mu bwoko bwa I ikajya mu bwoko bwa II, bigatuma habaho guhagarara kw'amaraso.
ECA2 nayo ifata phenylalanine ya amino acide ya carboxymeterine iva kuri angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kandi ikayishyira mu cyiciro cya angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-Gist-Pro-OH).
ECA2 kandi ifata indi peptide nyinshi zirimo [des-Arg9]-bradicinine, apeline, neurotensin, dinorphine A, na ghrelin.
ECA2 kandi igenzura gutwara imyenda ya SLC6A19 itwara amino acid idafite aho ihuriye kandi byerekanwe ko ifitanye isano n'indwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'umushinga wa transmembrane, ECA2 ikora nk'aho ingirabuzimafatizo y'ibanze mu nsoro za virusi zimwe na zimwe za corona, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ku gice cya ECA2 cya enzymatic ku gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo bituma virusi na enzyme biva mu bice by'imbere mu ngirabuzimafatizo bikinjira mu bice by'imbere.
