Isuzuma ry'imikorere n'ibipimo byatanzwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 byasanze "imikoreshereze y'imiti ya ACE yari ifitanye isano n'igabanuka ry'ibyago byo kurwara icyorezo cya Pneumonia ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'abagenzuzi".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara pneumonia byagabanutse no mu barwayi bavurwa na ACE inhibitors bari bafite ibyago byo kurwara pneumonia, cyane cyane abafite stroke n'umutima udakora neza.
Gukoresha inhibiteur ya ACE nabyo byari bifitanye isano no kugabanya urupfu rufatika rufatika rufatika ku ndwara ya pneumonia, nubwo ibisubizo byari bike cyane ugereranyije n'ibyago byose byo kurwara pneumonia".
