Igihe cy'igice cya kabiri cy'umwimerere cy'umwimerere cya rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha agera kuri 10 kandi intangiriro y'igikorwa ni iminota 30 nyuma y'igihe cy'ingaruka (igihe) cy'amasaha 24.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwinshi byerekana ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe ku bantu batagaragaza ubukana bw'imiti ya classical renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa mu ndwara ziteza ingufu z'imiti ya angiotensin II.
Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za porogaramu zigendanwa zo gufasha gukurikirana mu gusubiza icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-2020, ni ukuvuga igikorwa cyo kumenya abantu ("abahuye") bashobora kuba barahuye n'abantu banduye.
Hariho porogaramu nyinshi zagiye zitegurwa cyangwa zitanzweho inkunga y'ubutegetsi mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Ibikorwa bitandukanye byo gukora porogaramu zo kugenzura imibonano byatangiye gukorwa.
Ibibazo by'ibanga byavutse, cyane cyane ku miterere ishingiye ku gukurikirana ahantu hakorerwa porogaramu.
Ibindi byoroshye harimo gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kumenya aho ari hafi y'andi matelefone.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byombi byatangaje ko bizashyira hamwe imikorere yo gushyigikira porogaramu nk'izi zishingiye kuri Bluetooth kubikorwa byabo bya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba barahuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
Ubu ikoreshwa mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapuru, hari porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether ikoreshwa.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango wa IT wo muri ako gace, yasohotse nk'umushinga ufunguye kandi ugiye gushyikirizwa leta. Macedonia y'Amajyaruguru yatangije "StopKorona!", porogaramu ishingiye kuri Bluetooth igamije gukurikirana abantu bashobora kwandura no gutanga igisubizo cyihuse ku bategetsi b'ubuzima.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itangazamakuru n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kuva tariki ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu bari bahuye nayo iri mu cyiciro cy'iterambere kandi ko izaboneka mu byumweru. Porogaramu nk'iyi iteganyijwe muri Ireland no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid").
Australia na Nouvelle Zelande biteganya porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether ya Singapore na BlueTrace. Uburusiya buteganya gushyiraho porogaramu yo kugabanya aho abantu barwaye COVID-19 baba i Moscou, igamije kubafasha kuguma mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu buryo bw'ingirakamaro ku bihereranye n'imitegekere ishingiye ku porogaramu, hakubiyemo n'ibimenyetso by'uko ari ibinyoma, n'uko ishobora kutagira icyo igeraho mu gihe porogaramu yakwemerwa n'abantu bake cyane.
Mu gusubiza impungenge ku gukwirakwiza porogaramu za "coronavirus" z'ibinyoma cyangwa zangiza, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus ku bubiko bwayo bwa App, ikabigarurira gusa "amashyirahamwe yemewe" cyangwa andi yubahwa.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashyigikiye ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo kugenzura abantu benshi bakoresheje porogaramu za coronavirus, cyane cyane niba ibikorwa remezo by'iperereza byashyizweho mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus bizasenywa igihe iterabwoba rizaba ryarashize.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura.
Amashyirahamwe yatangaje ibintu umunani by'ibanze ku mishinga ya leta:
kugenzura byagombye kuba 'bikwiriye, bikenewe kandi bihuje n'amategeko';
kongera igihe cyo kugenzura no kugenzura byagombye kuba bifite ingingo z'igihembwe;
ikoreshwa ry'amakuru ryagombye kugabanywa ku mpamvu za COVID-19;
umutekano n'ubwirinzi by'ibanga bigomba kurindwa kandi bigatangazwa nk'ibyangombwa bishingiye ku bimenyetso;
Igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga rigomba kwirinda ko ivangura n'igwingira byongerwa;
gusangira amakuru n'abandi bantu bigomba gushyirwa mu mategeko;
hagomba kubaho ubuziranenge ku ihohoterwa n'uburenganzira bw'abaturage bwo gusubiza ihohoterwa;
uruhare runini rw' 'abafite uruhare rukomeye' bose, harimo n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima rusange n'amatsinda y'abasizwe n'abandi, rwari gukenerwa. Chaos Computer Club (CCC) yo mu Budage na Reporters Without Borders (RSF) na bo bashyize ahagaragara urutonde rw'ibisubizo.
Gahunda yateguwe na Google/Apple igamije gukemura ikibazo cy'uburinzi burambye ikura uburyo bwo gukurikirana mu mikorere yabwo y'ibikoresho igihe bitakiri ngombwa.
Ibihugu bimwe byakoresheje uburyo bwo gukurikirana ahantu hashingiye ku muyoboro aho gukoresha porogaramu, bikuraho icyifuzo cyo gukuramo porogaramu no kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Israel, uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu hakoreshejwe umurongo w'ikoranabuhanga bwemewe.
Ibisubizo bishingiye ku muyoboro bifite uburyo bwo kubona amakuru y'ahantu hakoreshejwe ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga bifite ibibazo bikomeye by'ibanga.
Ariko, ntabwo sisitemu zose zifite seriveri z'ibanze zikeneye kubona amakuru yerekeye aho umuntu ari; sisitemu nyinshi zirinda ubuzima bwite zashyizweho kugirango zikoreshe seriveri z'ibanze gusa mu itumanaho (reba igice kiri hasi).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, uburyo butari bushingiye kuri porogaramu bwakoreshejwe mu gukurikirana abantu.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu imwe, iyi sisitemu yakusanyije amakuru yo gukurikirana ava mu bisata bitandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'amakuru y'ubucuruzi bw'ikarita, ikabihuza kugira ngo itange imiburo yoherejwe hakoreshejwe ubutumwa bw'umwimerere ku bantu bashobora kuba banduye.
Usibye gukoresha aya makuru mu kuburira abantu bashobora guhura n'iki cyorezo, leta yashyize ku mugaragaro amakuru y'aho umuntu aba, ibi bikaba byemewe kubera impinduka zikomeye mu mategeko agenga ibanga ry'amakuru nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS muri icyo gihugu.
Aya makuru aboneka ku mugaragaro binyuze muri porogaramu zitandukanye na site za interineti. Ibihugu birimo n'u Budage birimo gutekereza gukoresha uburyo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite cyangwa bw'ibanze.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, amakuru arambuye yari atarahishurwa.
Gukurikirana guhura no kurinda ubuzima bwite ni igitekerezo cyasobanuwe neza, gifite ibitabo byinshi by'ubushakashatsi byatangiye mu mwaka wa 2013. Kuva tariki ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi y'impuguke yagiye akora ku bisubizo byubahiriza ubuzima bwite, hakoreshejwe Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kugirango hamenyekane aho umuntu ari hafi y'ibindi bikoresho bya telefone.
Ariko kandi, PEPP-PT ni igikorwa cyo guhuza ingamba zigenga ikoranabuhanga hamwe n'uburyo bwo kubara, ntabwo ari protocol imwe. Porotokaramu z'ibanze zirimo Decentralized privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Temporary Contact Numbers (TCN, fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN) Privacy Sensitive Protocols and Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT) n'izindi.
Muri izo porotokaramu, amakuru y'umuntu bwite ntajya ava mu gikoresho, kandi ibyo umuntu ahurizaho byose biba byakozwe mu gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'ibanga muri MIT Media Lab ryakoze Safe Paths, urubuga rwo gukoresha uburyo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite mu gihe cyo gukusanya no gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari cyangwa inzira z'inzira zo guhura kugira ngo bakurikirane ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu kinyamakuru cy'ikoranabuhanga cyitwa "Apps Play Dirty: Guteza imbere ubuzima bwite mu gihe cy'icyorezo" cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga rifite umutekano kugira ngo rifashe abakoresha gusangiza abandi bakoresha n'abashinzwe ubuzima amakuru ahereranye n'aho umuntu ari ndetse n'ubuzima bwe, nta guhungabanya ubwiru bw'ayo makuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, ishyirahamwe ry'isi yose rya TCN Coalition ryashinzwe n'amatsinda yifatanyije mu buryo bw'ibanze kandi ahanini hakoreshejwe amabwiriza menshi, agamije kugabanya gutandukana, no gutuma habaho guhuza ku isi hose kw'ibikoresho byo kuburira no gukurikirana, ikintu cy'ingenzi mu kugera ku ikoreshwa ry'ubu buryo.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko BlueTrace protocol ikoreshwa na porogaramu yemewe ya leta yabaye isoko ryugurutse.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bigenzura urubuga rwa mobile rwa Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abantu, aho bavugaga ko bazirinda ubuzima bwite, bishingiye ku ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy na encryption yo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite.
Nanone kandi, banditse ibijyanye n'ikoranabuhanga rikomeye rikoreshwa muri iyo gahunda.
Nk'uko Apple na Google babivuga, iyi gahunda igomba gukorwa mu byiciro bitatu:
guteza imbere ibikoresho bizatuma leta ishobora gukora porogaramu zemewe zo gukurikirana virusi ya corona ariko bigakomeza ubuzima bwite
guhuza uyu muco by'ukuri muri iOS na Android; Google na Apple bateganya guhangana n'ibibazo by'iperereza bikomeje kandi byamaze igihe binyuze mu kubanza gukwirakwiza sisitemu binyuze mu kuvugurura sisitemu ikora, hanyuma nyuma bakaza kuyikuraho mu buryo bumwe igihe cyose iterabwoba rirangiye.
Gusubiza umuti mu mwanya (uzwi kandi nka drug reproposal, reperfiling, reassignment cyangwa therapeutic substitution) ni ugusubiza umuti wemewe kuvura indwara cyangwa indwara itandukanye n'iyo watangijwe mbere.
Iyi ni imwe mu nzira z'ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi zirimo gukorwa muri iki gihe mu rwego rwo gukora imiti yo kuvura COVID-19 ifite umutekano kandi ikora.
Ibindi bikorwa byo gushakisha birimo gukora uburyo bwo kuvura no gukingira COVID-19. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine zigera kuri 66 zishobora gukoreshwa, buri poroteyine ifite aho ifata.
Gusuzuma ibyo bintu by'ingenzi bituma haboneka uburyo bufatika bwo gukora umuti wa COVID-19 urwanya za poroteyine.
Muri poroteyine z'ingenzi SARS-CoV-2 igamije harimo papain-like protease, RNA-dependent RNA polymerase, helicase, S protein na ADP ribophosphatease.
Hussein A. A., et al., bize ibipimo bitandukanye by'imiti byasobanuwe neza kandi byasuzumwe ku buryo buhuje n'imiti yemewe isa cyane kugira ngo byongere umuvuduko mu guteza imbere imiti ikomeye ya SARS-CoV-2 mu cyiciro cy'ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu cyiciro cy'ubushakashatsi.
Chloroquine ni umuti urwanya malariya ukoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara zimwe na zimwe ziterwa n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chlorokine na hydroxychloroquine bifitanye isano ari mu miti ine iri kwigwa mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi rya Solidarity.
Guverineri wa New York Andrew Cuomo yatangaje ko ibizamini bya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine muri leta ya New York bizatangira ku ya 24 Werurwe. Ku ya 28 Werurwe, FDA yemereye ikoreshwa rya hydroxychloroquine sulfate na chloroquine phosphate binyuze mu ruhushya rw'ubutabazi (EUA).
Iyi miti ntabwo yemewe n'ikigo FDA cy'igerageza mu buvuzi, kandi yemewe binyuze muri AUE gusa nk'ubuvuzi bw'igerageza bwo gukoreshwa mu buryo bw'ubutabazi mu barwayi bari mu bitaro badashobora guhabwa imiti mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi.
CDC yavuze ko "imikoreshereze, ingano cyangwa igihe cy'imikorere ya hydroxychloroquine mu kwirinda cyangwa kuvura SARS-CoV-2" bitarafatwa.
Abaganga bavuze ko bakoreshaga iyo miti mu gihe "nta kundi byagenda".
Mu mujyi wa Istanbul, itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Turukiya barimo bakora ubushakashatsi buto ku mikoreshereze ya chlorokine ifatanyije na zinc, vitamine A, vitamine C na vitamine D.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye burimo gukorwa muri kaminuza ya Duke na kaminuza ya Oxford.
Ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya NYU Langone ririmo gukora igerageza ku bw'umutekano n'ingaruka zo gukoresha mu kwirinda hydroxychloroquine.
Ibizamini by'ubuvuzi by'Abashinwa i Wuhan na Shenzhen byavuze ko byerekanye ko favipiravir ari "igikorwa cy'ingirakamaro".
Mu mujyi wa Shenzhen, abarwayi 35 bagaragaje ko batanduye mu minsi 4 ku kigereranyo, mu gihe abarwayi 45 batigeze bahabwa imiti y'ubushakashatsi bari barwaye iminsi 11.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe i Wuhan ku barwayi 240 barwaye pneumonia, kimwe cya kabiri cyahawe favipiravir, ikindi kimwe cya kabiri cyahawe umifenovir.
Ikigo cy'Ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani cyibukije abaturage ko ibimenyetso bihari byo gushyigikira iki kiyobyabwenge ari bike kandi ari ibisanzwe.
Ku ya 2 Mata, Ubudage bwatangaje ko buzagura imiti mu Buyapani kugira ngo bayishinge, hanyuma bukoreshe igisirikare kuyishyikiriza ibitaro bya kaminuza aho izakoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Nk'uko South China Morning Post ibivuga, Shinzo Abe yagiye ashyiraho uburyo bwo gufungura uburyo bwo kugura iki kiyobyabwenge, ariko ngo gishobora kuba kitagikora neza mu gihe cy'uburwayi bukomeye, ubwo virusi imaze kwiyongera.
Gukoresha uyu muti bishobora kuba bidakingiwe abagore batwite cyangwa abagore bagerageza gusama.
