Ibyo na byo bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cyo mu mutwe nyuma yo gukira.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, ntibari bazi niba ubwandu bwa kera bwatanga ubwirinzi bw'igihe kirekire ku bantu bakize.
Ubwirinzi bufatwa nk'ubusanzwe, hashingiwe ku myitwarire y'izindi koronavirusi, ariko hari inkuru zavuzwe z'abantu bakira COVID-19 bakongera bakageragerezwa koronavirusi nyuma yaho.
Ibi bibazo byitezwe ko ari byo bibi kurusha kwandura indwara mu gihe kirekire aho kuba kongera kuyandura.
Bivugwa ko virusi ari kamere kandi ko yakomotse ku nyamaswa, binyuze mu kwandura binyuze mu kwanduza.
Aho byaturutse ntiharamenyekana, ariko guhera mu Ukuboza 2019, ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu ryabaye hafi ya byose biturutse ku kwanduzanya umuntu ku wundi.
Ubushakashatsi ku bantu 41 ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19, bwanditswe muri Mutarama 2020 mu kinyamakuru The Lancet, bwagaragaje ko itariki ya mbere ibimenyetso byatangiriyeho ari tariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019.
Ibitabo by'ubutegetsi bya OMS byavuze ko itariki ya mbere ibimenyetso byatangiriyeho ari tariki ya 8 Ukuboza 2019.
Hari ingero nyinshi zikoreshwa mu gupima umubare w'abapfa.
Iyi mibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi bigira ingaruka ku mubare w'ibipimo, ubwiza bw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe cyashize kuva icyorezo cyatangira, n'ibintu biranga abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima muri rusange.
Mu mpera za 2019, OMS yahaye kode z'indwara z'ikibazo cya CID-10 U07.1 ku bapfuye bazize SARS-CoV-2 bamaze kwemezwa mu ma laboratwari na U07.2 ku bapfuye bazize COVID-19 bafite icyorezo cyangwa icyorezo, badafite SARS-CoV-2 bamaze kwemezwa mu ma laboratwari.
Hashingiwe ku mibare ya kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, umubare w'abapfa ku isi yose wari 6.9% (153.822/2.240.191) ku ya 17 Mata 2020.
Umubare utandukanye bitewe n'akarere. Ibindi bipimo birimo igipimo cy'ubwandu ku bantu (CFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu basanganywe indwara bapfa bazize indwara, n'igiciro cy'ubwandu ku bantu (IFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye (basanganywe indwara n'abatazifashwe) bapfa bazize indwara.
Izi mibare ntabwo ari iy'igihe gusa, kandi ikurikirana abaturage runaka kuva banduye kugeza ikibazo gikemutse.
Nubwo atari abantu bose banduye bagira udukoko tw'umubiri, kuba dufite utwo dukoko bishobora gutuma tumenya umubare w'abantu banduye.
Mu mujyi wa Castiglione d'Adda, mu Butaliyani, umujyi muto w'abantu 4.600, 80 (1,7%) bamaze gupfa.
Muri Gangelt, iyi ndwara yaturutse mu minsi mikuru ya Carnival, ikwirakwira mu rubyiruko, ituma abantu bapfa bagabanuka, kandi si ko abantu bose bapfuye bazira COVID-19 bashobora kuba barayihamijwe.
Byongeye kandi, sisitemu y'ubuzima mu Budage ntiyari yaremerewe.
Mu Buholandi, abantu bagera kuri 3% bashobora kugira udupfukamunwa, nk'uko byagaragaye mu batanga amaraso.
69 (0.004% by'abaturage) nibo bamaze kwemezwa ko bapfuye bazira COVID-19.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo n'umubare wacyo w'abapfa bitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Urupfu ruruta urw'abagabo mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani.
Ibyago bikomeye ku bagabo ni abo mu kigero cy'imyaka 50, aho itandukaniro hagati y'abagabo n'abagore rigenda rigera hafi ku myaka 90.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa wari 2.8 ku ijana ku bagabo, naho ku bagore ukaba 1.7 ku ijana.
Impamvu nyayo zituma habaho itandukaniro hagati y'ibitsina ntiziramenyekana, ariko ibintu by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima n'imyitwarire bishobora kuba ari byo bituma habaho itandukaniro.
Itandukaniro ry'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri rishingiye ku gitsina, kugabanuka kw'umubare w'abagore banywa itabi, no kuba abagabo baragize ibibazo by'amaraso nk'umuvuduko w'amaraso mu gihe bari bakiri bato kurusha abagore, bishobora kuba byaratumye abagabo bapfa cyane.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye bari abagabo, na 72% by'abapfuye bazira COVID-19 bari abagabo.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, leta ya Amerika ntiyari ikurikirana amakuru y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bufitanye isano n'imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara ziterwa na virusi, urugero nka Ebola, SIDA, ibicurane na SARS, zigira ingaruka ku bagabo n'abagore mu buryo butandukanye.
Umubare munini w'abakora mu by'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, ni abagore, kandi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi virusi.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 ko izina ry'ubuvuzi ari "COVID-19".
Umuyobozi wa OMS, Tedros Adhanon Ghebreyesus yasobanuye ko "CO" ari "corona", "VI" ari "virusi", "D" ari indwara, naho "19" ari igihe iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Izina ryatowe kugira ngo birinde kuvuga ahantu runaka (urugero: Ubushinwa), inyamaswa cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, hakurikijwe inama mpuzamahanga zo gushyiraho amazina yo kwirinda gutukana. Virusi itera COVID-19 yiswe SARS-CoV-2.
OMS ikoresha kandi "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi itera COVID-19" mu gutangaza amakuru ku baturage.
Indwara n'agakoko byombi bikunze kwitwa "coronavirus".
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabereye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byakunze kwitwa "coronavirus" na "coronavirus ya Wuhan".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yashyizeho "2019-nCov" na " 2019-nCoV indwara y'ubuhumekero" nk'amazina y'agateganyo ya virusi n'indwara, hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo mu 2015 yo kwirinda gukoresha imyanya mu mazina y'indwara na virusi.
Amazina yemewe ya COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Kubera ko ubushobozi bufite aho bugarukira mu byuma bitanga ibyangombwa, hari abahanga mu gukora ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki barimo gucapura ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, urugero nk'ibikoresho byo mu mazuru n'ibikoresho byo mu nda.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byari bikeneye cyane valve y'ubwonko, kandi umutangabuguzi atashoboraga kuyitanga ku gihe, ikigo cyo muri ako karere cyatangiye gukora ubuhanga bwo guhindura ibintu, maze gicapura valve 100 zari zikenewe mu kanya nk'ako guhumbya.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19, ibitekerezo by'ubugambanyi, amakuru atari yo n'amakuru atari yo ku nkomoko, ubukana, kwirinda, kuvura n'ibindi byerekeye indwara, byarakwirakwiriye kuri interineti.
Bisa n'aho abantu bashobora kwanduza virusi ku zindi nyamaswa zimwe na zimwe.
Ubushakashatsi ntibushobora kubona ibimenyetso by'uko virusi yongeye kwiyongera mu ngurube, mu du na mu nkoko.
Nta muti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe kuvura iyi ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku nkingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 burakomeje mu bigo bya leta, mu matsinda y'intiti n'abashakashatsi mu by'inganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije "SOLIDARITY Trial" kugira ngo rigerageze kureba ingaruka zo kuvura hakoreshejwe imiti ine irimo kurwanya virusi ishobora kuba ifite ingaruka nziza.
Nta rukingo ruboneka, ariko inzego zitandukanye zirimo gukora mu buryo bwihuse inkingo z'abakandida.
Ibikorwa bya mbere kuri SARS-CoV birakoreshwa kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuntu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira bukomeje gukorwaho ubushakashatsi.
Mbere na mbere, abashakashatsi bifuza gukora urukingo rukoresha virusi yose.
Gukoresha iyi virusi, yaba idafite ingufu cyangwa yapfuye, bigamije gutuma umubiri w'umuntu ugira uburyo bwihuse bwo kwirinda indwara nshya ya COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, ni urukingo rw'icyiciro cya kabiri, rugamije gukora urukingo rutuma abarwayi b'umubiri bagira ubushake bwo kurwanya ibice runaka bya virusi.
Ku kibazo cya SARS-CoV-2, ubwo bushakashatsi bwibanda kuri poroteyine yo mu musarani ifasha virusi kwinjira mu gikoresho cya ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni ubw'inkingo za aside ya nucleic (inkingo za ADN cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo gukora inkingo).
Inkingo z'igerageza kuri buri imwe muri izo ngamba zagombaga kuba zigomba kugeragezwa ku birebana n'umutekano n'ingaruka. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, ikigeragezo cya mbere cy'inkingo cyatangiye ku bantu bane bitangiye gukora mu mujyi wa Seattle.
Urukingo rurimo kode ya jenoside itagira icyo itwaye ikururwa na virusi iteza indwara.
Hari ibizamini birenga 300 by'ubuvuzi biri gukorwa kuva muri Mata 2020.
Ibizamini birindwi byasuzumye imiti yemewe ya malariya, harimo n'icyigisho cya hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Ihererekanya ry'imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi ni ryo rigizwe n'ubushakashatsi bwinshi mu Bushinwa, aho mu bihugu bitandukanye habera ibizamini by'ubushakashatsi mu cyiciro cya gatatu cy'imiti ya remdesivir, bikaba ari icyenda, nk'uko raporo yo mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa kane ibigaragaza.
Isuzuma ry'imikorere y'imiti n'urukingo bya COVID-19 byari mu kwezi kwa Mata 2020. Imiti itandukanye ya virusi irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir, chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir na lopinavir/ritonavir bifatanyije na interferon beta.
Hariho kugerageza kwemeza ko umuti wa remdesivir ufite akamaro kuva muri Werurwe 2020.
Ihinduka mu buvuzi ryabonetse mu barwayi bavurwa na remdesivir mu gihe cy'imikoreshereze y'impuhwe.
Ibizamini by'icyiciro cya III birimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Chloroquine, isanzwe ikoreshwa mu kuvura malariya, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, ibisubizo by'ibanze bikaba byaragaragaye.
Nyamara hari ibyifuzo byo gusubiramo icyi gitabo.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya no mu Bushinwa batanga inama yo gukoresha chlorine.
Nyamara, Ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe Virology, n'ubwo gitanga inama y'umushora wa gramu imwe ku munsi, kiraburira ko inshuro ebyiri z'uwo mugati ari akaga cyane kandi ko zishobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yashyize ahagaragara uruhushya rw'ikoreshwa ry'ibanze rya hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine ku buryo bw'ibanze ku baganga bavura abantu bafite COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko ingano nini ya ribavirin ikenewe mu kubuza SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitashakanijwe ko yakomeza kwiga in vivo nyuma yo kugaragaza ko ifite ubushobozi buke bwo gukumira SARS-CoV-2.Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko poroteyine y'umushongi w'intangiriro mu gutegura serine transmembrane protease 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ingenzi mu kwinjira kwa SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhuza na ACE2 receptor.
Ubushakashatsi ku bwonko na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa ntayo bifite aho bigarukira cyane byabujije umuryango w'ubuvuzi gufata izi miti nta bushakashatsi bwimbitse. Oseltamivir ntabwo ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 in vitro kandi nta ruhare ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Igisebe cy'imiti gishobora kuba ari ikibazo mu bihe bya nyuma bya COVID-19 ikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira imiterere yo kurwanya cytocin. Tocilzumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa nyuma yo kurangiza ubushakashatsi buto.
Ikigeragezo cyo mu cyiciro cya 2 cyo mu rwego rw'igihugu kiri gukorwa mu Butaliyani, nyuma yo kugaragaza ko cyatanze umusaruro mwiza ku bantu bafite indwara ikomeye.
Iyo ihuriweho n'igenzura ry'amaraso rya ferritin yo mu maraso kugira ngo hamenyekane ibihuha bya cytokine, byitezwe ko byangiza ibyo bintu, bikaba bifatwa ko ari byo bituma bamwe mu bantu baba babikomerekeyemo bapfa.
Interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yemejwe na FDA hashingiwe ku nyigo z'ibibazo by'inyuma ku kuvura syndrome yo kurekura cytokine idakora kuri steroid iturutse ku mpamvu itandukanye, CAR T cell therapy mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu nta bimenyetso by'ubushakashatsi byakozwe ku buryo buteganyijwe kandi bw'amabwiriza y'ibanze bigaragaza ko tocilzumab ari umuti w'ingirakamaro wo kuvura CRS.
Kwimura udukoko tw'umubiri twanduye kandi tw'ibanze dutangwa n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bw'abakize COVID-19 ku bantu babukeneye birimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'uburyo butari ubw'inkingo bwo kuboneza urubyaro.
Ubwo buryo bwashyizwe mu igeragezwa rya SARS, ariko nta musaruro ufatika wabonetse.
Kugabanya virusi ni uburyo bwitezweho bwo gukora ku buryo antibodies zidakora zishobora guhuza ubwirinzi kuri SARS-CoV-2.
Ubundi buryo ariko, nk'imiti yifashishwa mu kurwanya udukoko tw'umubiri n'imiti yifashishwa mu guhangana n'imiti, bishobora kubaho.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura antibodies zidakora, urugero nko gukoresha antibodies za monoclonal zikozwe, burimo gukorwa.
Umusaruro wa serum yo gukira, igizwe n'igice cy'amaraso y'abarwayi bakira, kandi irimo udukoko tw'ubumara tw'iyo virusi, ushobora kwiyongera kugira ngo ikorwe vuba.
